(29, '2014-07-03', 1, 1, 15, 'Boating', '', 'sports/boating', 'Boating in Central Park', '<p><img style="float: right;" title="rowboat on the lake" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/loeb-boathouse.jpg" alt="rowboat on the lake" width="220" height="165" /></p>\r\n<p>Daily 10AM - 6PM<br />April - November<br />Weather Permitting</p>\r\n<p><strong>Rowboats</strong>: $15 per hour (cash only) + $3.00 for each add''l 15 minutes + $20 cash deposit<br />-Holds up to 4</p>\r\n<p><strong>Gondolas</strong>: $30 per 1/2 hour<br />-Holds up to 6</p>\r\n<p><strong>Reservations</strong>: (212) 517-2233</p>\r\n<p>Rent a boat at the&nbsp;<a title="Loeb Boathouse" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/loeb-boathouse.html">Loeb Boathouse</a>&nbsp;and row your way to the heart of the Central Park&nbsp;<a title="Lake" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/lake.html">Lake</a>, the second-largest body of water in Central Park that spans over 22-acres.</p>\r\n<p>The Loeb Boathouse has a fleet of 100 boats, each of which seats four people. Renting a&nbsp;is ideal as a&nbsp;<a title="Date ideas" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/activities/dating-ideas.html">date activity</a>, a&nbsp;<a title="Proposal" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/weddings/proposals.html">wedding proposal</a>,&nbsp;and also great for a&nbsp;<a title="central park picnic" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/activities/picnics.html">picnic</a>&nbsp;with friends.</p>\r\n<p>You''ll be able to get a closer view of water fowl that are hard to see from the shore, including the park''s famous egrets, herons, and loons. Children will also enjoy helping to row the boat.</p>\r\n<p>Rowboats are available for rental in good weather.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Classic Venetian Gondola tours are available with gondolier Andres Garcia. Experience the Lake in the way that it was originally designed for by&nbsp;<a title="frederick law olmsted" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/history/frederick-law-olmsted.html">Frederick Law Olmsted.</a></p>\r\n<p>Life jackets are provided by the Loeb Boathouse. Children under 12 must be accompanied by an adult.</p>', 'At twenty-two acres, the Lake in Central Park offers one of the most peaceful settings that exists in NYC. Grab your date and an oar, and see Central Park as you never have before! ', 'Central Park, NYC, New York City, Boathouse, Bow Bridge, Calvert Vaux, Central Park History, children, family programs, Frederick Law Olmsted, Frederick Olmsted, Loeb Boathouse, Olmsted, park, row boating, Tavern on the Green, weekend, Boating, row boats, gondola, central park lake, lake, central park boathouse, wedding proposal, boat picnic, picnic, bodies of water, rowboat, date ideas, central park date, romantic date, family activity, central park boats, boat rental, rent a boat, gondola ride, gondola rental, boat ride', 83.00, 21, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=7&amp;blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&amp;cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&amp;exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&amp;loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&amp;referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&amp;mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=a98c2241&cb=INSERT_RANDOM_NUMBER_HERE'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=7&n=a98c2241'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>\r\n', '', '', '', 'softball.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Boating', 'Boating', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(30, '2015-06-27', 1, 1, 15, 'Chess & Checkers', '', 'sports/chess-checkers', 'Chess & Checkers in Central Park', '<p>Chess and checkers in Central Park is one of New York&rsquo;s most well-known traditions. In addition to being speckled with tables ideal for a game, Central Park hosts some facilities specifically designed to encourage the playing of chess and checkers.</p>\r\n<p>Central Park&rsquo;s Chess and Checkers House is one of several visitors&rsquo; centers within the park. Though you can play chess in almost any New York City Park, only at the Chess and Checkers House can you borrow pieces for your game. The 24 tables surrounding this rustic pagoda are blessed with ample shade, ideal for a checkers game any time of year. If you don&rsquo;t have a player, the park staff will help you find one. This spot is frequented by those who play chess nearly every day. It is an excellent spot for chess neophytes to improve their games.</p>\r\n{{ADSPACE_300_250}}\r\n<p>On certain summer weekends, players young and old can enjoy the expertise of grandmaster chess players. These events, usually held on Saturdays, include lectures on chess strategy. Additionally, up to 30 players at a time play each grandmaster. This chess series is free for adults and children.</p>\r\n<p>Though a festival, tournament, special event, or dedicated chess facility like the Chess and Checkers House are all ideal and dedicated chess and checkers playing venues, it is also possible to play in many locations throughout the park. Some tables have chess boards already pre-imprinted. Alternatively, you can bring your own chess board and pieces and wait to be approached. Choose pieces that will withstand wind.</p>\r\n<p>2015 Grandmaster events:</p>\r\n<p>Joel Benjamin June 20, 2015 10:00AM - 3:00PM</p>\r\n<p>Irina Krush July 11, 2015 10:00AM - 3:00PM</p>\r\n<p>Lev ALbert August 29, 2015 10:00AM - 3:00PM</p>', 'The Chess and Checkers House in central Park is just a short distance to the southwest of the Dairy, perched on the large rock outcropping once known as the Kinderberg. Built in 1952 the octagonal red and cream colored brick structure has indoor as well as outdoor tables that attract play?ers of all ages and prowess.\r\n\r\n', 'Central Park, NYC, New York City, Chess, Checkers, chess & checkers house, weekend, weekend actvities, weekend family programs, Wollman Rink', 0.00, 0, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=7&amp;blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&amp;cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&amp;exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&amp;loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&amp;referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&amp;mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=a98c2241&cb=INSERT_RANDOM_NUMBER_HERE'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=7&n=a98c2241'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>\r\n', '', '', '', 'softball.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Chess & Checkers', 'Chess & Checkers', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(31, '2012-06-08', 1, 1, 15, 'Cross-Country Skiing', '', 'sports/cross-country-skiing', 'Cross-Country Skiing in Central Park', '<table border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right" bgcolor="#ffffff">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" bgcolor="#ffffff">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/sports/cross-country-skiing.jpg" alt="Cross-Country Skiing in Central Park" width="200" height="267" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<p align="right"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><strong>X-country skiing Graywracke</strong>, <em>by <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/members/profile10999.html">pinsand</a></em> </span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Gliding across snow strewn open spaces it is hard to remember one is in the middle of the world''s biggest cities.</p>\r\n<p>Yet every winter when Mother Nature graces Central Park with a mandatory 6&rdquo; and more of 	base snow many New Yorkers head out with their cross country skis. Hilly and flat terrains 	provide fun and some challenges to beginner and expert alike.</p>\r\n<p>Here are some suggestions for a unique urban winter treat:</p>\r\n<p>Many skiers head for Sheep Meadow, located mid Park towards the West Side from 66th up to 	69th Streets. For the historically curious two statues can be found here. One is the 19th century 	bust of Italian patriot Giuseppe Mazzini and the other a crouched Native American with his 	faithful dog entitled Indian Hunter.</p>\r\n<p>The Great Lawn offers 55 acres, from 79th Street to 85th Street, to trek through the mid Park. 	Here where Paul Simon and Art Garfunkel once gave a reunion concert, their popular hit &ldquo;The 	Sounds of Silence&rdquo; describes one of the joys of this winter activity.</p>\r\n<p>During summer the crack of a baseball bat is most often heard all through the North Meadow. 	Snow transforms baseball diamonds to glittering pathways for swooshing away a few hours 	around 97th Street in the mid Park area.</p>\r\n<p>Although no cross country ski rental facilities are in the city the good news is there is no fee to 	use your equipment in Central Park.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Location</strong>: Sheep Meadow, the Great Lawn, and other large meadows in Central Park.</p>\r\n<p><strong>When</strong>: Cross country skiing is allowed only when there is a base of snow of at least six inches.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0 0 20px; text-align: right;"><small>&mdash; Linda J. Bottjer</small></p>\r\n{{ADSPACE_300_250}}', 'CentralPark.com - Your first stop for information on Central Park and The Central Park Zoo!  Including extensive event listings, maps, attractions, sports, activities, history, essential info for tourists.', 'Central Park, NYC, New York City, ballfields, Balto, baseball, basketball, Belvedere Castle, Bethesda Fountain, Bethesda Terrace, bike, Boathouse, Bow Bridge, Calvert Vaux, Carousel, Central Park Conservancy, Central Park History, children, climbing wall, conservancy, family programs, Frederick Law Olmsted, Frederick Olmsted, Gates, Great Lawn, Greensward, Harlem Meer, Heckscher ballfields, Ice Skating, Imagine, Lasker Rink, Loeb Boathouse, merry-go-round, Metropolitan Museum, Obelisk, Olmsted, park, playground, public monuments, public park, Ramble, recreation programs, reservoir, rock climbing, row boating, running track, Sheep Meadow, skating, softball, Strawberry Fields, Tavern on the Green, tennis, tennis court, tours, Vaux, volunteer, volunteer programs, walking tours, wall climbing, weekend, weekend actvities, weekend family programs, Wollman Rink', 0.00, 0, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=7&amp;blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&amp;cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&amp;exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&amp;loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&amp;referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&amp;mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=a98c2241&cb=INSERT_RANDOM_NUMBER_HERE'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=7&n=a98c2241'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>\r\n', '', '', '', 'softball.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Cross-Country Skiing', 'Cross-Country Skiing', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(32, '2014-04-02', 1, 1, 15, 'Football', '', 'sports/football', 'Football in Central Park', '<p>Football lovers will enjoy playing on Central Park''s large and grassy <a title="North Meadow" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/north-meadow.html">North Meadow</a>, the only field in the park where football is permitted.</p>\r\n<p>Football can be played in the park from September to November.</p>\r\n<p>There are a couple of rules: Players cannot wear cleats, and flag football and touch football are the only types of football allowed in the park; tackle football is not permitted.</p>\r\n<p>Any small group can use available space on the <a title="North Meadow" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/north-meadow.html">North Meadow</a>. However, large groups, leagues, or people who want to play at a regularly scheduled time need to <a title="nycgovparks" href="http://www.nycgovparks.org/permits/sport-field" target="_blank">apply for a ballfield permit</a> from the NYC Department of Parks and Recreation. For more information please visit the Parks Department''s <a title="nycgovparks" href="http://www.nycgovparks.org/" target="_blank">official website</a> or call the Manhattan ballfield permit office at (212) 408-0234.</p>\r\n{{ADSPACE_300_250}}\r\n<p>If you are visiting Central Park and wish to play a game with friends, you don''t need a permit.</p>\r\n<p>You may also wish to contact a local football group and find out when they play.</p>\r\n<p>You must bring your own football, as well as rubber-soled shoes.</p>\r\n<p>If you don''t have football equipment, you can borrow a field day kit from the <a title="North Meadow Center" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/activities/north-meadow-center.html">North Meadow Recreation Center</a>; you only need to show a picture ID.</p>', 'Football lovers will enjoy playing on Central Park''s large and grassy North Meadow, the only field in the park where football is permitted. Football can be played in the park from September to November. ', 'Central Park, NYC, New York City, ballfields, ball fields, sports, football, touch football, football permit, sports in central park new york, football central park', 0.00, 0, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=7&amp;blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&amp;cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&amp;exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&amp;loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&amp;referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&amp;mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=a98c2241&cb=INSERT_RANDOM_NUMBER_HERE'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=7&n=a98c2241'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>\r\n', '', '', '', 'softball.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Football', 'Football', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(33, '2012-06-07', 2, 1, 15, 'Arsenal', '', 'attractions/arsenal', 'The Arsenal in Central Park', '<p>It is older than Central Park itself and represents New York''s eternal ability to reimage itself.  Begun initially to store arms and ammunition of the New York State Militia in 1848, the Arsenal has proven itself a chameleon building in serving the City in a vast array of ways.</p>\r\n<p>Located at 64th Street off Fifth Avenue, this brick structure has additionally served as a police station, a museum, a weather bureau and a zoo. Today it offers a free treat to visitors with an ever-changing art gallery located on its third floor.</p>\r\n<p>Now designated an official New York City Landmark, the Arsenal''s massive half octagonal tower and other medieval fortress-like Gothic details, combined with a cast iron American eagle over the doorway, was not always to everyone''s liking.  One resident in 1859 wrote that he wished the Arsenal could be destroyed by an accidental fire.&nbsp;The objections increased when live caged birds joined dinosaurs'' skeletons during the late 19th century at a time when the American Museum of Natural History was first housed there.</p>\r\n{{ADSPACE_300_250}}\r\n<p>Its usefulness has always been the Arsenal''s savior.  During the Great Depression it became the headquarters for the New York City Department of Parks and Recreation, which it continues to be along with housing numerous other agencies like the Central Park Administration, the New York Wildlife Conservation Society and The Parks Library.</p>\r\n<p>Inside the lobby, a multi-story mural created by 1930''s WPA artist Allen Saalburg depicts the Arsenal''s early history through colorful vignettes of soldiers in formation.</p>\r\n<p>With an advanced reservation, history buffs can see the original Greensward Plan which is the blueprint designed by Frederick Law Olmstead and Calvert Vaux for Central Park.</p>\r\n<p>More than 160 years later, the Arsenal is still an important warehouse for New York.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Public Information:</strong> (212) 360-1311<br /> <strong>Arsenal Gallery Exhibitions:</strong> (212) 360-8163</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0 0 20px; text-align: right;"><small>&mdash; Linda J. Bottjer</small></p>', 'Begun initially to store arms and ammunition of the New York State Militia in 1848, the Arsenal has proven itself a chameleon building in serving the City in a vast array of ways.', 'central park arsenal, arsenal police station, arsenal militia, historic buildings, arsenal gallery exhibitions', 22.80, 5, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=15&amp;blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&amp;cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&amp;exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&amp;loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&amp;referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&amp;mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=a026fe8a&cb=INSERT_RANDOM_NUMBER_HERE'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=15&n=a026fe8a'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>', '', '', '', 'lake800.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/aric-boyles.html">Aric Boyles</a>', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Arsenal', 'Arsenal', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:0