(69, '2009-05-19', 1, 1, 14, 'Wall Climbing', '', 'sports/wall-climbing', 'Wall Climbing', '<p>Wall climbing is sport whose popularity is rapidly expanding. Artificial walls are \r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right" bgcolor="#ffffff">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" bgcolor="#ffffff">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img src="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/sports/climbing-wall.jpg" border="0" alt="Climbing Wall in Central Park" width="200" height="167" align="right" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="right"><a href="http://centralparkblogger.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><em>John B. Moore</em> </span></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<p align="left"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><strong>Climbing Wall in Central Park.</strong> </span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nconstructed that attempt to mimic the surfaces found in the more advanced sport of Rock Climbing. Wall climbing is a great introduction and the perfect place to hone your skills of strength, balance and not falling off.</p>\r\n<p>Supervised wall climbing is available for adults and children (ages 8 and up) at the <a href="page.php?pid=55">North Meadow Recreation Center</a>. Bouldering also is available in Central Park.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Where:</strong> North Meadow Recreation Center, mid-Park at 97th Street.</p>\r\n<p><strong>When:</strong> Click on Recreation Programs/Adventure for dates and times of adult climbing instruction, and introduction to climbing classes, and open climbing sessions.</p>\r\n<p><strong>How:</strong> Fees vary, and registration is required. Call the North Meadow Recreation Center at (212) 348-4867 ext 14 for more information.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Permit Requirement:</strong> No permit required.</p>', 'Central Park features supervised wall climbing for adults and children (ages 8 and up) at the North Meadow Recreation Center. Bouldering also is available in Central Park. \r\n\r\n', 'Central Park, NYC, New York City, , wall climbing, weekend, weekend actvities, weekend family programs, rock climbing', 186.70, 62, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=7&amp;blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&amp;cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&amp;exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&amp;loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&amp;referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&amp;mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=a98c2241&cb=INSERT_RANDOM_NUMBER_HERE'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=7&n=a98c2241'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>\r\n', '', '', '', 'softball.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Wall Climbing', 'Wall Climbing', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(70, '2015-06-14', 1, 1, 15, 'Yoga', '', 'sports/yoga', 'Yoga in Central Park', '<p><img style="float: right;" title="central park yoga" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/unnamed.jpg" alt="central park yoga" width="200" height="150" /></p>\r\n<p>Take a yoga class with us in Central Park and enjoy practicing outside and on the grass!&nbsp;The Yoga Trail and founder Silvia Neri offer regular Vinyasa Yoga Classes for all levels.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Special Offer:</strong> Free Dopper water bottle to the first student to book each class! More details below.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Price</strong>:<br />$15</p>\r\n<p><strong> Where</strong>:<br />Meeting point is 15 min before class in front of the cafe <a title="le pain quotidien central park" href="https://goo.gl/maps/nfVzO" target="_blank">Le Pain Quotidien</a>&nbsp;inside Central Park, north side of Sheep Meadow.&nbsp;From there we''ll walk together to class location. Closest park entrance is W69th St.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Book Online</strong>:<br />Choose from Sat-Sun at 10:30AM and Mon-Thurs at 6:30PM using the calendar below:</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<script src="https://fareharbor.com/embeds/script/calendar-small/theyogatrail/items/1738/?lightframe=yes&amp;asn=centralpark"></script>\r\n</p>\r\n<p><span><img style="float: right;" title="dopper water bottle" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/dopper.jpg" alt="dopper water bottle" width="200" height="129" /><a href="http://theyogatrail.us8.list-manage2.com/track/click?u=5750f0b8c86ba69bc355b7592&amp;id=2a1d7020d8&amp;e=171acb4234" target="_blank"><strong>Dopper is our Sponsor</strong></a>&nbsp;this year! Be the first to book a reservation for any class</span><span>&nbsp;will&nbsp;receive a Dopper water bottle.&nbsp;</span>Reduce waste of plastic bottles by refilling your own Dopper! Tell us what color you prefer when you book your class online.</p>\r\n<p><span>{{ADSPACE_300_250}}</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>About</strong>:<br />Vinyasa Yoga combines breath and movement to cleanse and recharge the body while providing an energizing opportunity to re-connect to nature in the city. Unlock the tension in your body and relieve stress while building core strength with a mindful focus. Each class ends with final relaxation and meditation.</p>\r\n<p>The classes are meant to establish the foundation of the yoga practice with an emphasis on breathing and healthy pose alignment. They are open to all fitness levels and have a meditative approach but will still involve a good amount of movement and some sweat.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Notes:<br /></strong>Book online, arrive early, and bring a mat or request one in advance. Bathrooms available.</p>\r\n<p>Classes are by&nbsp;<a title="the yoga trail in central park" href="http://www.theyogatrail.com/" target="_blank">The Yoga Trail</a>&nbsp;and are&nbsp;led by founder Silver Neri.</p>\r\n<p>Yoga is a discipline that centers on ideas such as peacefulness, living in the moment, harmony with nature and gratitude. Central Park is an ideal venue for practicing yoga and you can work on any flat, grassy surface you can find.</p>\r\n<p>Some nice places for practicing yoga in Central Park include the&nbsp;<a title="Great Lawn" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/great-lawn.html">Great Lawn</a>,&nbsp;<a title="Sheep Meadow" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/sheep-meadow.html">Sheep Meadow</a>,&nbsp;<a title="North Meadow" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/north-meadow.html">North Meadow</a>, and&nbsp;<a title="Strawberry Fields" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/strawberry-fields.html">Strawberry Fields</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Join us for daily outdoor yoga classes in Central Park! All levels welcome. Enjoy the perfect setting to do yoga on the grass in New York City and be in harmony with nature. ', 'Central Park yoga, outdoor yoga, yoga poses, yoga positions, yoga stretching, yoga in central park, new york city yoga', 36.40, 8, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=7&amp;blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&amp;cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&amp;exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&amp;loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&amp;referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&amp;mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=a98c2241&cb=INSERT_RANDOM_NUMBER_HERE'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=7&n=a98c2241'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>\r\n', '', '', '', 'softball.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Yoga', 'Yoga', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
