(71, '2015-04-24', 1, 1, 15, 'Ice Skating', '', 'sports/central-park-ice-skating', 'Ice Skating in Central Park', '<h3>Ice Skating</h3>\r\n<p style="padding-right: 5px;">Thousands of New Yorkers and tourists from across the globe enjoy ice skating in Central Park each winter. After all, there''s nothing more serene than gliding across the ice with the city skyline in the background. Ice skating is fun, healthy, and could be the perfect way to spend a very romantic winter day or night. So grab your skates and enjoy!</p>\r\n<table style="background: #fff;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><a title="Ice Skating in Central Park" rel="lightbox-guide" href="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/photos/normal/72/wollman-rink.jpg"> <img style="border: 0pt none;" title="Wollman Rink" src="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/photos/normal/72/wollman-rink.jpg" alt="Ice Skating in Central Park" width="200" height="140" /> </a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: right; font-size: 10px;"><strong>Ice Skating in Wollman Rink</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: right; font-size: 10px;">by Ivonpless</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3 style="font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #555;"><strong><a style="text-decoration: none;" href="/guide/attractions/wollman-rink.html">Wollman Rink</a></strong></h3>\r\n<p>The Wollman Rink is located on the east side, very close to the Central Park Zoo. It offers ice hockey, a skating school, party facilities, skate rentals, and lockers. For more information, call (212) 439-6900.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Enter the Park at 59th and 6th Avenue or 59th and 5th Avenue.</p>\r\n<p><strong>HOURS:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Monday &amp; Tuesday</strong>:&nbsp;10:00am-2:30pm</li>\r\n<li><strong>Wednesday &amp; Thursday</strong>:&nbsp;10:00am-10:00pm</li>\r\n<li><strong>Friday &amp; Saturday</strong>:&nbsp;10:00am-11:00pm</li>\r\n<li><strong>Sunday</strong>:&nbsp;10:00am-9:00pm</li>\r\n<li><strong>Thanksgiving</strong>: 10:00am-7:00pm (holiday rates apply)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>PRICES:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Adults</strong>: $11.25 Mon-Thurs; $18.00 Fri-Sun</li>\r\n<li><strong>Children</strong>:&nbsp;(11 &amp; under): $6.00 Mon-Sun</li>\r\n<li><strong>Seniors</strong>: $5.00 Mon-Thurs; $9.00 Fri-Sun</li>\r\n<li><strong>Skate</strong> <strong>Rentals</strong>: $8.00 (tax included)</li>\r\n<li><strong>Lock</strong> <strong>Rental</strong>: $5.00 (plus $6.00 refundable deposit)</li>\r\n<li><strong>Spectator</strong> <strong>Fee</strong>: $5.00</li>\r\n<li>****Cash Only**** No Credit Cards</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: Hours and rates are subject to change. Call (212) 439-6900 or visit <a title="wollman rink central park" href="http://www.wollmanskatingrink.com" target="_blank">Wollman Rink''s Official Website</a> to confirm pricing and schedules.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style="background: #fff;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="left">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><a title="Ice Skating Rink" rel="lightbox-guide" href="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/sports/ice-skating-rink.jpg"> <img style="border: 0pt none;" title="Wollman Rink" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/sports/ice-skating-rink.jpg" alt="Ice Skating in Central Park" width="190" height="127" /> </a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: right; font-size: 10px;"><strong>Ice Skating Rink</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: right; font-size: 10px;">by <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/members/profiles/Lorry">LORRY</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table style="background: #fff;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><a title="Ice Skating in Central Park" rel="lightbox-guide" href="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/sports/ice-skating-in-central-park.jpg"> <img style="border: 0pt none;" title="Wollman Rink" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/sports/ice-skating-in-central-park.jpg" alt="Ice Skating in Central Park" width="190" height="127" /> </a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: right; font-size: 10px;"><strong>Ice Skating in Central Park</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: right; font-size: 10px;">by <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/members/profiles/Tim4Peace">TIM4PEACE</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;"><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;"><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;">{{ADSPACE_300_250}}</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong><a style="text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/lasker-pool-rink.html">LASKER RINK</a></strong></h3>\r\n<p>The Lasker Rink is located mid-Park between 106th and 108th Streets and converts from a swimming pool in the summer to an ice-skating rink during the winter months. It hosts skating, adult and youth hockey, lessons for all ages and abilities, skate rentals, and lockers. For more information, call 917-492-3856.</p>\r\n<p>Enter the Park at 110th and Lenox Avenue.</p>\r\n<p><strong>HOURS:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Monday - Thursday</strong>: 10:00am-3:45pm</li>\r\n<li><strong>Friday</strong>: 10:00am -11:00pm</li>\r\n<li><strong>Saturday</strong>: 1:00pm-11:00pm</li>\r\n<li><strong>Sunday</strong> 12:30pm-4:30pm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Note:&nbsp;</strong>During holidays or special events, the rink may have different hours. Check the <a title="Lasker Rink Calendar of Events" href="http://www.laskerrink.com/default.aspx?p=home&amp;e=6&amp;redirecturl=http%3a%2f%2fwww.laskerrink.com%2fdefault.aspx%3fp%3dDynamicModule%26pageid%3d335494%26ssid%3d233586%26vnf%3d1" target="_blank">Lasker Rink Calendar of Events</a>&nbsp;for details.</p>\r\n<p><strong>PRICES:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Adults</strong>: $7.50</li>\r\n<li><strong>Children</strong> (11 &amp; under): $4.00</li>\r\n<li><strong>Seniors</strong>: $2.25</li>\r\n<li><strong>Skate</strong> <strong>Rentals</strong>: $6.50 (tax included)</li>\r\n<li><strong>Lock Rental</strong>: $3.25&nbsp;(plus refundable $4.00 deposit, tax included)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Hockey classes as well as group and private skating school lessons are also offered at the Lasker Rink. And kids can have their birthday party on ice! Contact the Lasker Rink directly for more information. Visit&nbsp;<a title="lasker rink central park" href="http://www.wollmanskatingrink.com/main_lasker.htm" target="_blank">Lasker Rink''s Official Site</a> or call 917-492-3856 Ext 17.&nbsp;</p>', 'Ice skating in Central Park is easily one of the most picturesque activities to be enjoyed on a winter''s day or night. ', 'central park ice skating, ice skating in central park, ice skating ring, ice skating in central park new york, central park skating rink, ice skating rink, central park ice skate, wollman rink, lasker rink, ice skating', 205.10, 60, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=7&blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=a98c2241&cb=INSERT_RANDOM_NUMBER_HERE'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=7&n=a98c2241'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>\r\n', '', '', '', 'bethesda_winter.jpg', 'Peter Neide', '', '', 0, '', '', 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Ice Skating', 'Ice Skating', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(72, '2012-06-08', 1, 1, 15, 'In-line Skating', '', 'sports/in-line-skating', 'In-line Skating in Central Park', '<p>Central Park is full of miles of paved parkways that are ideal for inline skating. The most popular place to skate in Central Park is the Loop, which is closed to car traffic at all times except morning and evening rush hour on weekdays. It is easy to choose between two versions of the Loop - one is shorter and one is longer. The longer loop is 5 miles long, and the shorter one is 2.5 miles long. When you skate past the <a title="Loeb Boathouse" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/loeb-boathouse.html">Loeb Boathouse</a>, you will have the option to go right up Cat Hill, or bear left to stay on the smaller loop.</p>\r\n<p>Traffic on the Loop is one-way; you should travel it counterclockwise. If you''re not sure which way is correct, look for the large white arrows painted on the pavement. Never go clockwise, or the wrong way, on the Loop. This could cause an accident. If you absolutely must backtrack, go very slowly along the side or even on the grass if you can.</p>\r\n<p>It is very important to follow safety rules on the Loop and be mindful of other users on the trail, since the Loop is not just for inline skaters. During times when cars are allowed on the Loop, all other trail users must stay in the far right lane. Naturally, this means that the lane gets crowded during these times, so if you are a neophyte skater, consider skating at a different time. When the Loop is closed to cars, the far right lane is reserved for the user of joggers. At some spots, the Loop intersects with pedestrian paths, such as near the <a title="Obelisk" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/obelisk.html">Obelisk</a>.</p>\r\n<p>On some weekends, the park skate safety crew runs a free stopping clinic, which you should take advantage of if you''re new to skating.</p>\r\n{{ADSPACE_300_250}}', 'Central Park is the center for in-line skating in New York.  On a hot summer day, the Park is filled with thousands of skaters. ', 'Central Park, NYC, New York City, ballfields, Balto, baseball, basketball, Belvedere Castle, Bethesda Fountain, Bethesda Terrace, bike, Boathouse, Bow Bridge, Calvert Vaux, Carousel, Central Park Conservancy, Central Park History, children, climbing wall, conservancy, family programs, Frederick Law Olmsted, Frederick Olmsted, Gates, Great Lawn, Greensward, Harlem Meer, Heckscher ballfields, Ice Skating, Imagine, Lasker Rink, Loeb Boathouse, merry-go-round, Metropolitan Museum, Obelisk, Olmsted, park, playground, public monuments, public park, Ramble, recreation programs, reservoir, rock climbing, row boating, running track, Sheep Meadow, skating, softball, Strawberry Fields, Tavern on the Green, tennis, tennis court, tours, Vaux, volunteer, volunteer programs, walking tours, wall climbing, weekend, rollerblading, in-line skating, roller skating, Wollman Rink', 0.00, 0, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=7&amp;blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&amp;cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&amp;exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&amp;loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&amp;referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&amp;mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=a98c2241&cb=INSERT_RANDOM_