(90, '2015-07-21', 3, 1, 15, 'Concerts and Music', '', 'activities/concerts', 'Central Park Concerts and Music', '<table style="background: #ffffff;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #ffffff; width: 200px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img style="border: 0px;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/bon-jovi-concert-in-central-park.jpg" alt="Bon Jovi in Central Park" width="200" height="159" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: xx-small;" align="right"><strong>Bon Jovi Concert in Central Park</strong> by             <em><a href="http://www.centralpark.com/members/profiles/asterix" target="_blank">asterix</a></em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>If you''re looking for music in the summer, you&rsquo;ll find it all in New York''s Central Park.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Here are some of the most popular venues and concert series:</p>\r\n<p><strong>Rumsey Playfield<br /></strong><a title="summerstage rumsey playfield" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/summerstage.html">Rumsey Playfield</a>, located on the east side of the park near the entrance at E. 69th St. and Fifth Ave, is host to the annual SummerStage and "Good Morning America" concert series.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>SummerStage takes place from May to September and features a variety of music, from rock to pop to salsa, reggae, opera, and much more.Whatever your musical tastes, you can find something that you''ll like at SummerStage! Check out the&nbsp;<a title="schedule of summer stage performances" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/activities/concerts/summerstage-festival.html">schedule of performances</a>&nbsp;here.</p>\r\n<p>ABC''s "GMA" Summer Concert Series happens every Friday at Rumsey Playfield and airs live between 7 - 9AM. See the&nbsp;<a title="GMA summer concert series central park" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/activities/concerts/gma-concerts.html">schedule of performances</a>&nbsp;here.</p>\r\n<p><span><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;">{{ADSPACE_300_250}}</span></span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Naumburg Bandshell<br /></strong>The <a title="naumburg bandshell central park" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/bandshell.html">Naumburg Bandshell</a>&nbsp;is located mid-park between 66th and 72nd Streets. The modern Naumburg Bandshell replaces the original structure, which was built in 1862 exclusively for classical music, but it still continues the tradition of hosting classical music performances. Over the years, some more popular music events have been hosted here as well. You can see the schedule of the <a title="naumburg bandshell performances" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/activities/concerts/naumburg-orchestra.html">Naumburg Bandshell&rsquo;s performances</a> here.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Family Performance Festival &ndash; Fun for the Little Ones<br /></strong>If you&rsquo;re taking the kids to Central Park, the Family Performance Festival (free event) will get them to move and groove with everything from sing-along music to dance performances to story-time shows.&nbsp;<span>This year''s <a title="Family Performance Festival Central Park" href="http://www.centralparknyc.org/about/programs/family-performance-festival.html" target="_blank">Family Performance Festival</a> is chock-a-block full of fun and learning through music, storytelling, Park adventures, puppetry, and more!&nbsp; Programs happen every Sunday from mid June - September 6th at 12 noon, on the Great Hill (located inside the Park near West 103rd - 106th Street). Pack a picnic, grab your blanket, and get ready to discover Central Park in a whole new way!&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Impromptu Music for Summertime Strolls<br /></strong>One of the most famous street performers in Central Park is David Ippolito, also known as &ldquo;That Guitar Man from Central Park.&rdquo; On his website, David says he generally starts at 12:30 each day and ends when the sun goes down. You can view his schedule online at <a title="music central park" href="http://www.thatguitarman.com" target="_blank">http://www.thatguitarman.com/</a>.</p>\r\n<p>There are other street performers in Central Park as well, but some of the most popular venues for watching them have now been designated as <a title="quiet zones central park" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/general-info/quiet-zones-in-central-park.html">quiet zones</a>. One of these zones is the <a title="bethesda terrace" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/bethesda-terrace.html">Bethesda Terrace</a>, which had long been hailed by performers for its great acoustics. There are now eight&nbsp;<a title="quiet zones central park" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/general-info/quiet-zones-in-central-park.html">quiet zones</a>&nbsp;in the park which, in addition to&nbsp;<a title="bethesda terrace" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/bethesda-terrace.html">Bethesda Terrace</a>, include <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/conservatory-garden.html">Conservatory Garden</a>, <a title="conservatory water" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/conservatory-water.html">Conservatory Water</a>, East Green, <a title="shakespeare garden" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/shakespeare-garden.html">Shakespeare Garden</a>, <a title="sheep meadow" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/sheep-meadow.html">Sheep Meadow</a>, <a title="strawberry fields" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/strawberry-fields.html">Strawberry Fields</a> and <a title="turtle pond" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/turtle-pond.html">Turtle Pond</a>. So if you need a little break from all the music that you&rsquo;re hearing, these areas will provide you with the respite that you need.</p>\r\n<p>Overall, no matter what your musical tastes, you will likely be able to find performances that please your auditory senses. While some of the more organized music shows only take place during the summer, many of the street performers will continue throughout the winter months, so you can feel free to visit Central Park any time of the year to hear sounds that will delight your ears.</p>', 'Summer in Central Park brings lots of music and many free concerts. See the schedule for the annual SummerStage series at Rumsey Playfield, the GMA free Summer Concert Series, free performances by the New York Philharmonic and Metropolitan Opera on the Great Lawn, and also shows at the Naumberg Bandshell to name a few.', 'Concerts, SummerStage, Summer Stage, central park summer stage, central park summerstage, Central Park, NYC, New York City, concerts, music, philharmonic, naumberg orchestra, metropolitan opera, concerts on the great lawn, summer concerts central park, central park concerts, GMA summer concert series, good morning america summer concert series, rumsey playfield, free concerts central park, central park gam, central park good morning america, central park summer concert series', 64.10, 22, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=12&amp;blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&amp;cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&amp;exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&amp;loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&amp;referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&amp;mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=ab1f636b&cb=1233'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=12&n=ab1f636b'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>', '', '', '', 'meadow.jpg', '<a href="http://www.luminous-newyork.com">Joergen Geerds</a>', '', '', 12, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Concerts and Music', 'Concerts and Music', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(91, '2013-08-13', 3, 1, 15, 'Romantic Ideas', '', 'activities/romantic-ideas', 'Romantic Ideas in Central Park', '<p>Central Park, by its very nature, is one of the most romantic spots in New York City.    \r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right" bgcolor="#ffffff">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" bgcolor="#ffffff">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img src="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/activities/romantic.jpg" border="0" alt="Romantic Ideas in Central Park" width="220" height="146" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="right"><a href="page.php?pid=109"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><em>Rick Anderson</em></span></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<p align="left"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><strong>A Romantic interlude in Central Park.</strong> </span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nSoon after entering the park you feel your pace slow, a certain edginess leaves your body and your mind can wander just a bit. At the same time you are able to focus that much better on the person strolling at your side. Tree branches interlace the sky and you follow walkways that stretch ahead in soothing curves; you&rsquo;ve left behind the hard angles of avenues and the harsh reality of cement. Here your perception is filtered through a lens of diffuse clarity; your senses heightened, reflexes relaxed. The park becomes the perfect place for heartfelt declarations and, perhaps, subtle seduction.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Picnic in the Park</strong> &ndash; Pack a picnic lunch or light dinner, or have one prepared at one of the many specialty food shops that ring the park. Add a bottle of sparkling cider and toast the sunset from any one of the many lovely spots the park provides for blanket spreading. A favorite spot is Cherry Hill, just west of <a href="page.php?pid=37">Bethesda Fountain</a>. <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/store/central-park-picnic-backpack-p-50.html"><img style="width: 84px; height: 104px;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Central_Park_Backpack_for_Two_thumb.jpg" border="0" alt="" hspace="6" vspace="6" width="84" height="104" align="left" /></a>There you can relax on a gentle slope overlooking the lake and watch the rowboats glide along the glassy surface. Or just wander around and find your own favorite spot. And for the best possible picnic, make sure you stock up on <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/store/picnic-park-c-29.html">official CentralPark.com Picnic Stuff</a>!</p>\r\n<p><strong>Conservatory</strong><strong>Garden</strong> &ndash; Try a visit to the <a href="page.php?pid=41">Conservatory Garden</a>, a secluded Eden just east of the North Meadow. Take a seat under one of the flowering trees, for an added touch try reciting a poem, from memory if possible. Yes it&rsquo;s a bit corny, but it works. As long as you don&rsquo;t choose Dr. Seuss.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Walks</strong> &ndash; Take a walk through the <a href="page.php?pid=77">Shakespeare Garden</a> and then check out the view from <a href="page.php?pid=36">Belvedere Castle</a>. Stroll along the Mall up to <a href="page.php?pid=37">Bethesda Terrace</a>. <a href="page.php?pid=80">Strawberry Fields</a>, the <a href="page.php?pid=55">North Meadow</a> - the park offers endless possibilities for simply walking hand in hand and exploring the landscape.</p>\r\n<p><a href="page.php?pid=29"><strong>Rowboats</strong></a> &ndash; Try something classic - rent a rowboat at the Boathouse and row around the lake. Take a tour of the western end of the lake, north along the ramble or south around Wagner cove. Or just float about and marvel at the skyline as the sunsets over the West Side of Manhattan.</p>\r\n<p><a href="page.php?pid=71"><strong>Ice Skating</strong></a> - Ice skating in Central Park is easily one of the most picturesque and romantic, activities to be enjoyed on a winter&rsquo;s night. Feel the cold tingle of New York''s crisp winter air, listen to the music, and take in the incomparable surroundings as you glide (gracefully or not so) around the rink. Then share a hot chocolate and critique the other skaters from the terrace overlooking the rink.</p>\r\n<p><a href="page.php?pid=90"><strong>Concerts in the Park</strong></a> - Virtually every musical genre imaginable is featured at sometime and someplace during the summer months in Central Park. These include free performances by the New York Philharmonic and the Metropolitan Opera on the Great Lawn, Summerstage at Rumsey Playfield and the concert series at Naumburg Bandshell. What could be more romantic than relaxing on a blanket on the <a href="page.php?pid=45">Great Lawn</a>, listening to the New York Philharmonic and staring up into the sky.</p>\r\n<p><a href="page.php?pid=95"><strong>Dinner in the Park</strong></a>&ndash; Take a walk through the park and finish with a surprise dinner at the <a href="page.php?pid=108">Boathouse Restaurant</a>, but make sure to call ahead to check on reservations.</p>\r\n<p>Also see: <a href="page.php?pid=52">Dating Ideas</a></p>\r\n<p>And please use the comments buton at the top to share your favorite Romantic moments in Central Park</p>', 'Central Park, by its very nature, is one of the most romantic spots in New York City.  The Park offers almost endless ways to enjoy an intimate moment away from the stress of city life.', 'Romantic Ideas, Central Park, NYC, New York City, ballfields, Balto, baseball, basketball, Belvedere Castle, Bethesda Fountain, Bethesda Terrace, bike, Boathouse, Bow Bridge, Calvert Vaux, Carousel, Central Park Conservancy, Central Park History, children, climbing wall, conservancy, family programs, Frederick Law Olmsted, Frederick Olmsted, Gates, Great Lawn', 13.70, 3, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=12&amp;blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&amp;cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&amp;exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&amp;loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&amp;referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&amp;mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=ab1f636b&cb=1233'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=12&n=ab1f636b'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>', '', '', '', 'great_lawn_rick.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 46, '', '', 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Romantic Ideas', 'Romantic Ideas', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(92, '2015-06-01', 0, 0, 15, 'Weddings in Central Park', '', 'weddings', 'Central Park Weddings', '<div>\r\n<script src="https://fareharbor.com/embeds/api/v1/"></script>\r\n</div>\r\n<table style="background: #ffffff; margin-left: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 11px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img style="border: 1px solid #d0d0d0;" title="Weddings in Central Park" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/weddings-in-central-park.jpg" alt="Weddings in Central Park" width="185" height="190" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10px; line-height: 13px; padding-left: 2px" align="left">Jessica Schmitt Photography</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Central Park is one of the most romantic and picturesque places to have a wedding in New York City.</p>\r\n<p>Choose from wedding ceremony locations that feature some of the most iconic scenery in the city, such as the  	<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/conservatory-garden.html">Conservatory Garden</a>,  	<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/ladies-pavilion.html">Ladies Pavilion</a>,  	the <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/pond.html">Pond</a>,  	<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/cherry-hill.html">Cherry Hill</a>,  	<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/cop-cot.html">Cop Cot</a>,  	<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/belvedere-castle.html">Belvedere Plaza</a>, and&nbsp;<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/wagner-cove.html">Wagner Cove</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Our <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/weddings/ceremonies.html">Central Park Wedding Ceremony Package</a> is fully customizable to fit your needs and your budget.</p>\r\n<p>If you have an idea for your wedding that you don''t see listed, please <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/contact/wedding">contact us</a> to discuss!</p>\r\n<p class="alignC"><a class="noHoverBg oCTA" onclick="FH &amp;&amp; FH.open &amp;&amp; FH.open({ shortname: ''acentralparkwedding'', asn: ''centralpark'', view: { item: 3667 } }); return false;" href="https://fareharbor.com/acentralparkwedding/items/3667/"><img src="/usr/media/weddings/wedding-reserve-online-button.png" alt="reserve online" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>CentralPark.com has partnered with A Central Park Wedding to make planning all aspects of your special day a simple and enjoyable experience. We take care of everything for you from your permit to flowers to photography and more!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<script src="https://fareharbor.com/embeds/script/calendar-small/acentralparkwedding/items/3667/?lightframe=yes&amp;asn=centralpark"></script>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>We look forward to helping you plan your special day in New York City''s beautiful Central Park!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;">{{ADSPACE_300_250}}</span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Not allowed in Central Park</h3>\r\n<p>Chairs, tents, tables, rugs, runners, throwing of rice, birdseed, flowers, confetti, or anything else that will affect the soil is not allowed in Central Park. There are exceptions to the use of chairs for those who cannot stand for long periods of time. Alcohol, candles, or amplified sound are not allowed. Acoustic music is permitted.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Planning your own ceremony?</h3>\r\n<p>One of the most popular locations, the Conservatory Garden, located at Fifth Avenue and 105th Street requires a permit for ceremonies and photography sessions.  You can apply for your permit for the Conservatory Garden at the Central Park Conservancy by calling 212-360-2766 or you can  <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.centralparknyc.org/assets/pdfs/forms-and-applications/wedding-application.pdf">download the application online</a>. For any other location in Central Park, you can download the application from the NYC Department of Parks &amp; Recreation''s website. The maximum number of guests allowed for a ceremony in Central Park is 300. Each location has a specific guest limit.  If you plan to have less than 20 people at your wedding ceremony in a location outside of the Conservatory Garden, you are not required to purchase a permit. However, we highly recommend getting a permit to guarantee your space. You can also find more information in our  <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/weddings/ceremonies.html">Ceremonies</a>,  <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/weddings/proposals.html">Proposals</a>,  <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/weddings/receptions.html">Receptions</a> and  <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/weddings/faqs.html">Wedding FAQs</a> sections. We look forward to helping you plan your special day in New York City''s beautiful Central Park!</p>\r\n<p>Take our <a title="central park wedding poll" href="https://www.facebook.com/centralpark/app_126231547426086" target="_blank">wedding poll</a> and help us decide the best location to get married in Central Park!</p>', 'Central Park is a romantic and picturesque place to have a wedding. That''s why we''ve partnered with A Central Park Wedding to make planning all aspects of your special day in Central Park a simple and enjoyable experience. ', 'central park wedding, central park wedding ceremony, get married in central park, bethesda fountain, belvedere castle, wagner cove, cherry hill, carousel, central park boathouse, central park lake, conservatory garden, central park proposal', 20.00, 6, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=12&blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=ab1f636b&cb=1233'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=12&n=ab1f636b'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>', '', '', '', 'weddings-in-central-park.jpg', 'Fotovolia', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Weddings', 'Weddings', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(93, '2013-08-13', 3, 1, 15, 'Pets', '', 'activities/pets', 'Pets in Central Park', '<table style="background: #ffffff;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #ffffff; width: 200px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/activities/pets.jpg" border="0" alt="Pets" width="200" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: xx-small;" align="right"><strong><a href="http://nycphotonews.com/" target="_blank">NYCPhotoNews</a></strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Pets are most welcome in Central Park, as long as they and their owners follow Park rules and regulations.</p>\r\n<ul class="bullet">\r\n<li>Dogs must be leashed from 9AM - 9PM each day and at all times when in the woodland areas of the Park.</li>\r\n<li>Dog drinking fountains are available and are located at various spots throughout the Park.</li>\r\n{{ADSPACE_300_250}}\r\n<li>Dogs cannot dig or play in the flowerbeds, nor drink or play in fountains or any other bodies of water.</li>\r\n<li>Pet owners must clean up after their pets at all times and in all areas of the Park.</li>\r\n<li>There are 23 noted dog-friendly areas.</li>\r\n<li>Dogs must be on-leash at all times in the following locations:        \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Arthur Ross Pinetum</li>\r\n<li>Bridle Path</li>\r\n<li>Cedar Hill</li>\r\n<li>Conservatory Garden</li>\r\n<li>Kerbs Boathouse Plaza</li>\r\n<li>Shakespeare Garden</li>\r\n<li>Strawberry Fields</li>\r\n<li>Turtle Pond Lawn</li>\r\n<li>Woodlands</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Dogs are not allowed in the following locations:        \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ballfields</li>\r\n<li>East Green</li>\r\n<li>Elm Islands at the Mall</li>\r\n<li>Great Hill Glade</li>\r\n<li>Lilac Walk</li>\r\n<li>Ornamental Fountains</li>\r\n<li>Playgrounds</li>\r\n<li>Reservoir Running TrackPlaygrounds</li>\r\n<li>Sand Volleyball Court</li>\r\n<li>Sheep Meadow</li>\r\n<li>Water Bodies</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Central Park Paws is an organization that holds events specially for dog owners and their pets.  Consider joining Paws and participating in year-round events at Central Park.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="margin: 0 0 20px; text-align: right;"><small>&mdash; Jesse M. Wheeler </small></p>', 'Pets are most welcome in Central Park, as long as they and their owners follow Park rules and regulations.', 'Pets, Dogs, Cats, Park rules and regulations', 8.40, 2, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=12&blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=ab1f636b&cb=1233'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=12&n=ab1f636b'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>', '', '', '', 'great_lawn_rick.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 38, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Pets', 'Pets', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(94, '2009-05-19', 3, 1, 14, 'Zoo', '', 'activities/zoo', 'Central Park Zoo', '<p>The <a href="page.php?pid=87">Central Park Zoo</a> offers a perfect venue for a family \r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right" bgcolor="#ffffff">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" bgcolor="#ffffff">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img src="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/zoo/redpanda1[1].jpg" border="0" alt="Red Oanda in Central Park" width="139" height="200" align="bottom" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="right"><a href="http://www.maryschwalm.com/"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><em>Mary Schwalm</em> </span></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<p align="left"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><strong>A Red Panda in the  <br />Central Park Zoo.</strong> </span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nvisit to the park. It is divided into several different sections that provide the animals with homes as close to their natural habitat as possible. These include tropic, temperate and polar zones that house everything from tiny <a href="page.php?pid=127">leafcutter ants</a> to the hugely popular <a href="page.php?pid=113">polar bears</a>. The zoo is also actively involved the preservation of endangered species, providing a home for rare <a href="page.php?pid=133">tamarin monkeys</a>, <a href="page.php?pid=125">Wyoming toads</a>, <a href="page.php?pid=137">thick-billed parrots</a>, and <a href="page.php?pid=121">red pandas</a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Location</strong> : East Side between 63rd and 66th Streets</p>\r\n<p><strong>Details </strong> <br /> Hours: April - Oct. Monday - Friday 10 am - 5 pm, Weekends 10 am - 5:30 pm;  Nov. - March Daily 10 a.m. - 4:30 p.m. <br /><br />- Admission to Wildlife Center  includes admission to Children''s Zoo: Adults $8.00; Senior Citizens (65+) $4;  Children 3-12 $3.00; Children under 3, Free <br /><br />- General Information:  212-439-6500 <br /></p>', 'The Zoo in Central Park offers a perfect venue for a family visit to the park. It is divided into several different sections that provide the animals with homes as close to their natural habitat as possible. ', 'Zoo, Central Park Zoo, Central Park, NYC, New York City, ballfields, Balto, baseball, basketball, Belvedere Castle, Bethesda Fountain, Bethesda Terrace, bike, Boathouse, Bow Bridge, Calvert Vaux, Carousel, Central Park Conservancy, Central Park History, children, climbing wall, conservancy, family programs, playground, public monuments, public park, recreation programs, weekend', 40.20, 13, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=12&amp;blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&amp;cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&amp;exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&amp;loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&amp;referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&amp;mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=ab1f636b&cb=1233'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=12&n=ab1f636b'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>', '', '', '', 'great_lawn_rick.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Zoo', 'Zoo', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(95, '2014-06-12', 3, 1, 15, 'Central Park Restaurants', '', 'activities/restaurants', 'Central Park Restaurants', '<p>Central Park offers a variety of locations for park goers to pick up a snack, sit down to a formal dinner or even spread out with a&nbsp;<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/activities/picnics.html">picnic</a>.</p>\r\n<p>There are several outdoor concession stands scattered throughout the Park:</p>\r\n<p><a href="page.php?pid=86"><strong><br />Wollman Rink</strong></a>, East 63rd Street Mid-Park<br /><strong><a href="page.php?pid=94"><br /></a>Leaping Frog Caf&eacute;</strong>, across from the Arsenal, East 64th Street at Fifth Avenue<br /><strong><br /><a href="page.php?pid=40">Kerbs Ice Cream Caf&eacute;</a></strong> at Conservatory Water, East 74th Street near the Perimeter<br /><strong><br />Ferrara</strong><strong> Italian Caf&eacute;</strong> at Merchants'' Gate, West 61st Street and Central Park West<br /><strong><br />Ballplayers House</strong>, 65th Street at Mid-Park next to the <a href="page.php?pid=39">Carousel<br /><br /></a></p>\r\n{{ADSPACE_300_250}}\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Central Park also has several full service restaurants:</p>\r\n<p><a href="page.php?pid=78"><strong>Sheep Meadow Caf&eacute;</strong></a> at Mineral Springs, East 69th Street at the East Drive, offers a more casual dining experience.<br /><strong><br />Le Pain Quotidien</strong> at Mineral Springs Pavilion near 69th Street serves soups, salas and sandwiches and  offers an outside terrace.<br /><br /><a href="page.php?pid=108"><strong>Loeb Boathouse</strong></a>, East 74th Street at the East Drive, offers a full menu and service al fresco.<a href="page.php?pid=83"><strong><br /><br />Tavern on the Green</strong></a>, West 66th Street and Central Park West, is a more formal restaurant with brilliant d&eacute;cor and a choice several different rooms in which to dine.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Central Park offers a variety of locations for park goers to pick up a snack or sit down to a formal dinner.', 'Central Park Restaurants, Dining in the Park, restaurants, Central Park, NYC, New York City, ballfields, Balto, baseball, basketball, Belvedere Castle, Bethesda Fountain, Bethesda Terrace, bike, Boathouse, Bow Bridge, Calvert Vaux, Carousel, Central Park Conservancy', 7.20, 2, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=12&amp;blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&amp;cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&amp;exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&amp;loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&amp;referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&amp;mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=ab1f636b&cb=1233'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=12&n=ab1f636b'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>', '', '', '', 'great_lawn_rick.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 41, '', '', 0, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Restaurants in Central Park', 'Restaurants in Central Park', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(96, '2015-07-07', 3, 1, 15, 'Restaurants Around Central Park', '', 'activities/restaurants-around-central-park', 'Restaurants Around Central Park', '<p>Visitors have many dining options even before entering Central Park. Good restaurants, from casual to fine dining and everything in between, are abundant in the Central Park area. Some of these favorites include:</p>\r\n<ol class="arabic">\r\n<li> <img style="border: 3px solid #fff; margin: 0 0 5px 5px;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/activities/restaurants/south-gate.jpg" alt="South Gate" height="60" align="right" /> <strong><a href="http://www.southgaterestaurantnyc.com/" target="_blank">SOUTHGATE Bar &amp; Restaurant</a></strong>&nbsp;<sup>$$$$</sup><br /><span style="font-size: 10px;"><strong>Location</strong>: 154 Central Park South</span> <br />\r\n<p><span>SOUTHGATE offers a variety of unique, delicious flavors in an upscale, inviting atmosphere. Located in the heart of Manhattan, with spectacular Central Park views, a cozy fireplace and a talented staff of first-rate chefs.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li> <strong><a href="http://www.parkermeridien.com/eat4.php" target="_blank">Burger Joint at Le Parker Meridien</a></strong> <sup>$</sup><br /><span style="font-size: 10px;"><strong>Location</strong>: 119 W 56th St</span> <img style="border: 3px solid #fff; margin: 0 0 5px 5px;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/activities/restaurants/burger-joint.jpg" alt="Burger Joint at Le Parker Meridien" height="60" align="right" />\r\n<p>Located inside the lobby of the Le Parker Meridien Hotel, the Burger Joint boasts the best burgers in New York City.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li> <strong><a href="http://www.rue57.com" target="_blank">Rue 57</a></strong> <sup>$$$</sup><br /><span style="font-size: 10px;"><strong>Location</strong>: 60 West 57th St #1</span> <img style="border: 3px solid #fff; margin: 0 0 5px 5px;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/activities/restaurants/rue-57.jpg" alt="" height="60" align="right" />\r\n<p>Rue 57 offers French and Japanese cuisine and even functions as a Steakhouse.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li> <strong><a href="http://www.marea-nyc.com/" target="_blank">Marea</a></strong>&nbsp;<sup>$$$$</sup><br /><span style="font-size: 10px;"><strong>Location</strong>: 240 Central Park South</span> <img style="border: 3px solid #fff; margin: 0 0 5px 5px;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/activities/restaurants/marea.jpg" alt="Marea" height="60" align="right" />\r\n<p><span>Marea&nbsp;Ristorante, located in one of Manhattan''s most storied addresses, features Chef Michael White''s ode to Italian seafood.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li> <strong><a href="http://www.malaganyc.com/" target="_blank">Malaga</a></strong> <sup>$$$</sup><br /><span style="font-size: 10px;"><strong>Location</strong>: 406 E 73rd St #1</span> <img style="border: 3px solid #fff; margin: 0 0 5px 5px;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/activities/restaurants/malaga-restaurant.jpg" alt="Malaga" height="60" align="right" />\r\n<p>A bit further from Central Park than others on this list, a trip to Malaga is worth it for this restaurant''s intimate, romantic atmosphere and authentic Spanish cuisine.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n{{ADSPACE_300_250}}\r\n<ol class="arabic" start="6">\r\n<li> <img style="border: 3px solid #fff; margin: 0 0 5px 5px;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/activities/restaurants/sarabeths.jpg" alt="Sarabeth''s" height="60" align="right" /> <strong><a href="http://www.sarabethscps.com/" target="_blank">Sarabeth''s</a> </strong> <sup>$$$</sup><br /><span style="font-size: 10px;"><strong>Location</strong>: 40 Central Park South</span>\r\n<p>Known for its delicious brunch, Sarabeth''s is a great place to bring kids.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li> <img style="border: 3px solid #fff; margin: 0 0 5px 5px;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/activities/restaurants/cafe-sabarsky.jpg" alt="Caf&eacute; Sabarsky" height="60" align="right" /> <strong><a href="http://www.neuegalerie.org/cafes/sabarsky" target="_blank">Caf&eacute; Sabarsky</a></strong> <sup>$$$</sup><br /><span style="font-size: 10px;"><strong>Location</strong>: 1048 5th Avenue</span>\r\n<p>Caf&eacute; Sabarsky often features live jazz music is the perfect place to enjoy Viennese specialties.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li> <strong><a href="http://www.21club.com/web/onyc/21_club.jsp" target="_blank">21 Club</a></strong> <sup>$$$$</sup><br /><span style="font-size: 10px;"><strong>Location</strong>: 21 West 52nd St</span> <img style="border: 3px solid #fff; margin: 0 0 5px 5px;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/activities/restaurants/21club.jpg" alt="21 Club" height="60" align="right" />\r\n<p>American cuisine served in a setting that''s both sophisticated and fun. Dine in the famous Bar Room or the romantic Upstairs at 21.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li> <strong><a href="http://siriony.com/" target="_blank">Sirio</a></strong>&nbsp;<sup>$$$$</sup><br /><span style="font-size: 10px;"><strong>Location</strong>: 795 5th Avenue</span> <img style="border: 3px solid #fff; margin: 0 0 5px 5px;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/activities/restaurants/sirio.jpg" alt="Sirio" height="60" align="right" />\r\n<p><span>At Sirio Ristorante, contemporary interpretations of traditional Italian dishes inspired by the Tuscan standards of Maccioni&rsquo;s youth are served in a beautiful and engaging environment.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li> <strong><a href="http://www.metmuseum.org/visit/plan-your-visit/dining-at-the-museum/roof-garden-cafe-and-martini-bar" target="_blank">Met Roof Garden Cafe &amp; Martini Bar</a></strong> <sup>$$</sup><br /><span style="font-size: 10px;"><strong>Location</strong>: 1000 5th Ave, Fl 5</span><strong><br /></strong> <img style="border: 3px solid #fff; margin: 0 0 5px 5px;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/activities/restaurants/met-roof.jpg" alt="Met Roof Garden Cafe &amp; Martini Bar" height="60" align="right" />\r\n<p>A rooftop garden that overlooks Central Park with a small but adequate food and drink menu for such amazing views. Open May through late fall, weather permitting: Friday and Saturday: 10:00 AM &ndash; 8:00 PM.; Martini Bar: 5:30 &ndash; 8:00 PM; Sunday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday: 10:00 AM &ndash; 4:30 PM; Closed Mondays.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="margin: 0 0 20px; text-align: right;"><small>&mdash; Jesse M. Wheeler </small></p>', 'Good restaurants, from casual to fine dining and everything in between, are abundant in the Central Park area. Here are some delicious options to get you started:', 'restaurants around central park, dining, eating, food, brasserie, central park restaurants', 5.80, 3, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=12&blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=ab1f636b&cb=1233'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=12&n=ab1f636b'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>', '', '', '', 'great_lawn_rick.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick 