(101, '2015-05-29', 3, 1, 15, 'Central Park Film Festival', '', 'activities/central-park-film-festival', 'Central Park Film Festival', '<p><img style="float: right;" title="central park film festival" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/cpfilmfestival_lit.jpg" alt="central park film festival" width="200" height="133" /></p>\r\n<p>Each year in August, the Central Park Conservancy hosts a week of free evening film screenings.</p>\r\n<p>This year in 2015, the festival takes place from August 25-29.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-weight: bold;">2015 Central Park Film Festival Schedule.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>The event is FREE and all films will be shown rain or shine:</p>\r\n<p>Tuesday, August 25:&nbsp;<a title="Fame" href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0080716/" target="_blank">Fame</a>&nbsp;1980 (R)<br />Wednesday, August 26:&nbsp;<a title="The Blues Brothers" href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0080455/?ref_=nv_sr_1" target="_blank">The Blues Brothers</a>&nbsp;1980 (R)<br />Thursday, August 27:&nbsp;<a title="Airplane" href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0080455/?ref_=nv_sr_1" target="_blank">Airplane</a>&nbsp;1980 (PG)<br />Friday, August 28:&nbsp;<a title="Raging Bull" href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0081398/?ref_=nv_sr_1" target="_blank">Raging Bull</a>&nbsp;1980 (R)<br />Saturday, August 29:&nbsp;<a title="Superman II" href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0081573/" target="_blank">Superman II</a>&nbsp;1980 (PG)</p>\r\n<p><em>More details about the festival can be found below:</em></p>\r\n<p><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;"><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;"><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;"><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;"><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;"><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;"><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;"><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;"><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;"><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;"><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;">{{ADSPACE_300_250}}</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Time</strong>: Gates open at 6:30pm.&nbsp;All movies begin at 8:00pm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Location</strong>: The festival will be held just north of the Sheep Meadow, between Sheep Meadow and the 72nd Street Cross Drive (Enter mid-Park at E. 69th St.)</p>\r\n<p><strong>What to Bring</strong>: Bring a picnic and a blanket.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-style: italic;"><strong>What NOT to Bring:</strong><em>&nbsp;</em>G</span><span style="font-style: italic;">lass bottles, video cameras, tape recorders, chairs and alcoholic beverages are not allowed. All bags may be searched.</span></p>', 'Every August, the Central Park Conservancy hosts a week of free evening film screenings in Central Park. Bring a blanket and a picnic and enjoy watching a movie under the stars. ', 'Central Park Film Festival, sheep meadow, films, movies, outdoor movies in central park, central park movies, central park films, central park movie festival, movies in the park', 12.70, 4, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=12&amp;blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&amp;cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&amp;exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&amp;loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) docume