(180, '2013-08-19', 167, 3, 15, 'Kid''s Stuff', '', 'activities/children-s-activities/playgrounds/kid-s-stuff', 'Kid''s Stuff in Central Park', '<p>For those moments when you can''t be at the park here''s some fun things to pass the time while you''re waiting for your next visit.</p>\r\n<!-- <a href="http://www.thecentralparkboathouse.com/sections/home.htm" mce_href="http://www.thecentralparkboathouse.com/sections/home.htm" target="_blank"><img hspace="3" height="102" width="170" vspace="3" border="0" align="right" alt="The Boathouse Restaurant Central Park" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/ads/theboathouselogo._NEW.jpg" mce_src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/ads/theboathouselogo._NEW.jpg" /></a>-->\r\n<p><br /><a href="http://www.nycgovparks.org/sub_things_to_do/park_planner.html" target="_blank">Design Your Own Park</a>: Ever want to design your own park? Well here''s your chance courtesy of the New York City Parks Department. <br /><br /><a href="http://www.nps.gov/yell/forkids/index.htm" target="_blank">Yellowstone National Park Kid''s Page</a>: Check out some fun things to do at one of our most amazing national Parks. <br /><br /><a href="http://www.arrowscape.co.uk/schools/fun.htm" target="_blank">Fun Links fron Arrowscape</a>: Here is a great collection of links brought to you by our friends in Great Britain. <br /><br /><a href="http://www.kids.gov/k_funstuff.htm" target="_blank">First Gov for Kids</a>: An amazing collection of educational and (really) fun things to do brought to you by the Government of the United States of America. Wow. <br /><br />{{ADSPACE_300_250}}<br /><br /><a href="http://www.nga.gov/kids/zone/zone.htm" target="_blank">The Art Zone for Kids</a>: Interactive art work that you can create online! <br /><br /><a href="http://georgewashington.si.edu/kids/portrait.html" target="_blank">George Washington Portrait for Kids</a>: Follow the clues and help solve a make-believe mystery! <br /><br /><a href="http://www.smithsonianeducation.org/students/idealabs/amazing_collections.html" target="_blank">Smithsonian Collecting for Kids</a>: Visit <strong>Kids Collecting</strong> and explore the riches of the Smithsonian&rsquo;s collections. <br /><br /><a href="http://pbskids.org/cyberchase/index.html" target="_blank">PBS Cyberchase</a>: Play interactive games and crack challenging puzzles, meet the characters, and experience original adventures.</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.curiocabinetspot.com/kids-guide-to-collecting">A Kids Guide to Collecting Things</a>: Learn how to become a bona fide collector of cool stuff!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'CentralPark.com - Your first stop for information on Central Park and The Central Park Zoo!  Including extensive event listings, maps, attractions, sports, activities, history, essential info for tourists.', 'Kids, Children, Central Park, NYC, New York City, ballfields, Balto, baseball, basketball, Belvedere Castle, Bethesda Fountain, Bethesda Terrace, bike, Boathouse, Bow Bridge, Calvert Vaux, Carousel, Central Park Conservancy, Central Park History, climbing wall, conservancy, family programs', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', 'carousel.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Kid''s Stuff', 'Kid''s Stuff', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
