(259, '2008-02-08', 0, 0, 16, 'Tiger Woods ''06', '', '', 'Tiger Woods ''06', '<img height=\\"37\\" alt=\\"golf_in_central_park.gif\\" src=\\"http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/golf/golf_in_central_park.gif\\" width=\\"400\\" align=\\"baseline\\" border=\\"0\\" /> <br />\r\n<table cellspacing=\\"3\\" cellpadding=\\"0\\" width=\\"190\\" align=\\"right\\" bgcolor=\\"#ffffff\\" border=\\"0\\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\\"center\\">\r\n            <table cellspacing=\\"0\\" cellpadding=\\"0\\" align=\\"right\\" bgcolor=\\"#ffffff\\" border=\\"0\\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td><img height=\\"135\\" alt=\\"tiger_swing.jpg\\" src=\\"http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/golf/tiger_swing.jpg\\" width=\\"180\\" align=\\"baseline\\" border=\\"0\\" /></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>\r\n                        <p><font size=\\"1\\"><strong>Tiger Woods lining up on the 9th hole in Central Park!</strong></font></p>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>You\\''re on the 9th green, a hush comes over the crowd as you line up your putt. You take a deep breath and try not to notice Tiger Woods staring at you intently from just beyond the right bunker. You\\''re just about to three putt for a birdy and the lead going into the back nine when you\\''re startled by the clatter of hooves. You smile at the crowd and wait patiently as the bright red horse-drawn carriage jangles by above you at the top of Bethesda Terrace. Yes that Bethesda Terrace, the one in Central Park. A mid-afternoon daydream? Maybe, but if this scene isn\\''t reality, it is now a virtual reality, thanks to Tiger Woods and EA Games. </p>\r\n<br /><br /><img height=\\"36\\" alt=\\"golf_headline3.gif\\" src=\\"http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/golf/golf_headline3.gif\\" width=\\"300\\" border=\\"0\\" /> <br /><br />\r\n<table style=\\"MARGIN: 0px 5px 5px 0px\\" cellspacing=\\"3\\" cellpadding=\\"0\\" align=\\"left\\" bgcolor=\\"#ffffff\\" border=\\"0\\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\\"center\\">\r\n            <table cellspacing=\\"0\\" cellpadding=\\"0\\" align=\\"left\\" bgcolor=\\"#ffffff\\" border=\\"0\\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td align=\\"center\\"><img height=\\"135\\" alt=\\"lake.jpg\\" src=\\"http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/golf/lake.jpg\\" width=\\"180\\" align=\\"baseline\\" border=\\"0\\" /></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td align=\\"center\\">\r\n                        <p align=\\"left\\"><font size=\\"1\\"><strong>The Central Park Lake. <br />Just another tricky water hazard <br />found in Tiger Woods PGA Tour \\''06.</strong> </font></p>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>With the release of Tiger Woods PGA Tour 06 Central Park Course EA gives all of us, avid duffers and tyros alike, the chance to play a round of golf that takes you up and down the width and breadth of Central Park. With graphics that are incredibly true to the topography of the real park this game gives you the opportunity to site see around the most beautiful part of the Big Apple, while competing on a course designed by Tiger Woods himself. And it\\''s probably the only course outside of Scotland that finishes next to a castle. That would be Belvedere Castle, just off the 18th green, around 80th St.</p>\r\n<table align=\\"right\\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><img height=\\"200\\" alt=\\"box.gif\\" hspace=\\"5\\" src=\\"http://www.boyles.us/cp.com/box.gif\\" width=\\"170\\" vspace=\\"5\\" border=\\"0\\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\\"center\\"><img height=\\"20\\" alt=\\"buy.gif\\" hspace=\\"5\\" src=\\"http://www.boyles.us/cp.com/buy.gif\\" width=\\"104\\" border=\\"0\\" /> </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\\"CLEAR: both\\"><a href=\\"http://www.easports.com/games/tigerwoods06/home.jsp\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Click here to play golf with Tiger Woods in Central Park!</a> </p>', 'CentralPark.com - Your first stop for information on Central Park and The Central Park Zoo!  Including extensive event listings, maps, attractions, sports, activities, history, essential info for tourists.', 'Central Park, NYC, New York City, ballfields, Balto, baseball, basketball, Belvedere Castle, Bethesda Fountain, Bethesda Terrace, bike, Boathouse, Bow Bridge, Calvert Vaux, Carousel, Central Park Conservancy, Central Park History, children, climbing wall, conservancy, family programs, Frederick Law Olmsted, Frederick Olmsted, Gates, Great Lawn, Greensward, Harlem Meer, Heckscher ballfields, Ice Skating, Imagine, Lasker Rink, Loeb Boathouse, merry-go-round, Metropolitan Museum, Obelisk, Olmsted, park, playground, public monuments, public park, Ramble, recreation programs, reservoir, rock climbing, row boating, running track, Sheep Meadow, skating, softball, Strawberry Fields, Tavern on the Green, tennis, tennis court, tours, Vaux, volunteer, volunteer programs, walking tours, wall climbing, weekend, weekend actvities, weekend family programs, Wollman Rink, Central Park Zoo', 0.00, 0, '<a href=\\"http://www.easports.com/games/tigerwoods06/home.jsp\\" target=\\"blank\\">\r\n\r\n<IMG height=\\"600\\" alt=\\"ad.jpg\\" \r\nsrc=\\"http://www.boyles.us/cp.com/ad.jpg\\" width=\\"160\\" border=\\"0\\"></a>\r\n', '', '', '', 'default.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/aric-boyles.html">Aric Boyles</a>', '', 'golf.php', 0, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Tig