(271, '2014-11-07', 0, 0, 15, 'Hotels', '', 'hotels', 'Central Park Hotels', '<p>Looking for Central Park-convenient hotel accommodations in New York? Here you can find information about hotels located in the heart of New York City. Whether you''re planning a family vacation or business trip, there is a hotel for every taste and budget.</p>\r\n<!-- START HOTEL SEARCH --> <noscript id="_noscript" style="border: 1px dashed #f00; background: #FFFFBF; padding: 4px; color: #f00;">Please activate javascript for correct visualization of the searchbox</noscript> <form id="frmHotelsSearch" style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #d0d0d0; padding: 10px;" action="http://www.booking.com/searchresults.html" method="get"> <input name="error_url" type="hidden" value="http://www.booking.com/index.en.html?aid=334464" /> <input name="ssai" type="hidden" value="1" /> <input name="ssre" type="hidden" value="1" /> <input id="availcheck" name="do_availability_check" type="hidden" value="on" /> <input name="aid" type="hidden" value="334464" /> <input name="lang" type="hidden" value="en" /> <input name="ifl" type="hidden" value="1" /> <input name="si" type="hidden" value="ai,co,ci,re" /> <input name="label" type="hidden" value="hotels_page" /> <input name="landmark" type="hidden" value="15346" /> <input name="radius" type="hidden" value="2" />\r\n<p><strong>When are you planning your visit to New York City?</strong></p>\r\n<div style="margin: 2px 0;"><label style="font-weight: bold;" for="hotels_checkin_year_month">Check-in date</label> <select id="hotels_checkin_year_month" style="width: 75px;" name="checkin_year_month"> <option>Month</option> </select> <select id="hotels_checkin_monthday" style="width: 50px;" name="checkin_monthday"> <option>Day</option> <option>1</option><option>2</option><option>3</option><option>4</option><option>5</option><option>6</option><option>7</option><option>8</option><option>9</option><option>10</option><option>11</option><option>12</option><option>13</option><option>14</option><option>15</option><option>16</option><option>17</option><option>18</option><option>19</option><option>20</option><option>21</option><option>22</option><option>23</option><option>24</option><option>25</option><option>26</option><option>27</option><option>28</option><option>29</option><option>30</option><option>31</option> </select></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 2px 0;"><label style="font-weight: bold;" for="hotels_checkout_year_month">Check-out date</label> <select id="hotels_checkout_year_month" style="width: 75px;" name="checkout_year_month"> <option>Month</option> </select> <select id="hotels_checkout_monthday" style="width: 50px;" name="checkout_monthday"> <option>Day</option> <option>1</option><option>2</option><option>3</option><option>4</option><option>5</option><option>6</option><option>7</option><option>8</option><option>9</option><option>10</option><option>11</option><option>12</option><option>13</option><option>14</option><option>15</option><option>16</option><option>17</option><option>18</option><option>19</option><option>20</option><option>21</option><option>22</option><option>23</option><option>24</option><option>25</option><option>26</option><option>27</option><option>28</option><option>29</option><option>30</option><option>31</option> </select></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: right;margin-top: -25px"><input style="font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1px;" type="submit" value="Search" /></div>\r\n</form> <!-- END HOTEL SEARCH -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style="background: #ffffff; margin: 5px 0 5px 5px;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #ffffff; width: 200px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img style="border: 0px;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/6C_Studio_King.jpg" alt="6 Columbus" width="200" height="150" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: xx-small;" align="right"><strong>6 Columbus</strong> by <em><a onclick="target=''_blank''" href="http://www.thompsonhotels.com/" target="_blank">SIXTY Hotels</a></em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><a title="6 Columbus Thompson Hotel New York Central Park" href="http://www.booking.com/hotel/us/6-columbus-a-thompson.en-us.html?aid=334464" target="_blank">6 Columbus</a> &ndash;&nbsp;<span>Discover downtown chic on the luxurious edge of Midtown Manhattan. SIX Columbus &ndash; a SIXTY Hotel infuses its 1960&rsquo;s modernist d&eacute;cor with is 21</span><sup>st</sup><span>&nbsp;century sensibility and style. Located on the cusp of Central Park, adjacent to Columbus Circle and the Time Warner Center and just steps from 5</span><sup>th</sup><span>&nbsp;Avenue and Times Square, this 4-star boutique hotel showcases the award-wining signature restaurant Blue Ribbon Sushi, a guest-only roof top lounge bar, &nbsp;and a selection of rooms and suites with terraces and Central Park views.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<table style="background: #ffffff; margin: 5px 0 5px 5px;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #ffffff; width: 200px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/hotels/hotels-jw-marriott.jpg" border="0" alt="JW Marriott Essex House" width="200" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: xx-small;" align="right"><strong>JW Marriott Essex House</strong> by <em><a onclick="target=''_blank''" href="http://www.thefiftybest.com">The Fifty Best</a></em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>With an ideal location on Central Park South, the <a title="JW Marriott Essex House hotel new york central park" href="http://www.booking.com/hotel/us/j-e-house-new-york-new-york.en-us.html?aid=334464" target="_blank">JW Marriott Essex House</a> features on-site dining options, a full-service spa, and a 24-hour gym.</p>\r\n<table style="background: #ffffff; margin: 5px 0 5px 5px;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #ffffff; width: 200px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/hotels/hotels-trump-suite.jpg" border="0" alt="Trump International Hotel &amp; Tower" width="200" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: xx-small;" align="right"><strong>Trump International Hotel &amp; Tower</strong> by <em><a onclick="target=''_blank''" href="http://www.hotelchatter.com">Hotel Chatter</a></em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Each spacious room at <a title="Trump International Hotel New York Central Park West" href="http://www.booking.com/hotel/us/trump-international-new-york.en-us.html?aid=334464" target="_blank">Trump International New York</a> on Central Park West provides kitchenette facilities and boasts views of the city or Central Park.</p>\r\n<table style="background: #ffffff; margin: 5px 0 5px 5px;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #ffffff; width: 200px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/hotels/hotels-hilton.jpg" border="0" alt="West 57 Street by Hilton Club" width="200" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: xx-small;" align="right"><strong>West 57 Street by Hilton Club</strong> by <em><a onclick="target=''_blank''" href="http://www.timesharejuice.com">timesharejuice</a></em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>The <a title="Hilton Club West 57th New York Central Park" href="http://www.booking.com/hotel/us/west-57th-street-by-hilton-club.html?aid=334464" target="_blank">Hilton Club West 57th</a> offers studio and suite accommodations along with an on-site spa. Located at the top of Time Warner Center, <a title="Mandarin Oriental Hotel New York Central Park" href="http://www.booking.com/hotel/us/mandarin-oriental.en-us.html?aid=334464" target="_blank">Mandarin Oriental New York</a> is one block from Central Park. It features a 75-foot indoor pool and offers rooms with panoramic views of Manhattan.</p>\r\n<p>Another top luxury property, only steps from the park, is <a href="http://www.booking.com/hotel/us/the-pierre-a-taj.en-us.html?aid=334464" target="_blank">The Pierre</a>. This legendary, historic hotel also features the latest in modern conveniences.</p>\r\n<table style="background: #ffffff; margin: 5px 0 5px 5px;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #ffffff; width: 200px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/hotels/hotels-mandarin.jpg" border="0" alt="Mandarin Oriental" width="200" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: xx-small;" align="right"><strong>Mandarin Oriental</strong> by <em><a onclick="target=''_blank''" href="http://en.escapio.com">Escapio</a></em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.booking.com/hotel/us/the-empire.en-us.html?aid=334464" target="_blank">The Empire</a> is also a chic, boutique hotel option. Located between Lincoln Center and Central Park, the rooftop pool and bar is one of its most distinctive features.</p>\r\n<p>A good budget option is the <a title="comfort inn central park west" href="http://www.booking.com/hotel/us/comfort-inn-central-park-west.en.html?aid=334464" target="_blank">Comfort Inn Central Park West</a>. Only one block from Central Park, this hotel offers a continental breakfast, on-site gym and free in-room Wi-Fi.</p>\r\n<p>A popular tourist hotel, centrally located blocks from Central Park, theaters, Carnegie Hall and Fifth Avenue shopping is the <a href="http://www.booking.com/hotel/us/wellington-manhattan.en-us.html?aid=334464" target="_blank">Wellington Hotel</a>.</p>\r\n{{ADSPACE_300_250}}\r\n<p>For a more homey experience, try <a href="http://www.booking.com/hotel/us/strawberry-fields.en-us.html?aid=334464" target="_blank">The Central Park Bed and Breakfast</a>. This guesthouse is just steps from Central Park and each room features a microwave and refrigerator. The&nbsp;<a href="http://www.booking.com/hotel/us/park-79.en-us.html?aid=334464" target="_blank">Park 79 Hotel</a>&nbsp;also offers guests a more residential feel. Only the <a title="museum of natural history" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/activities/museums/american-museum-of-natural-history.html">American Museum of Natural History</a> separates it from Central Park, and coffee and tea are provided daily in the lobby.</p>\r\n<p>Once you find your Central Park hotel, check out some of the nearby <a title="Central Park Attractions" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions.html">Central Park attractions</a> including <a title="Central Park Belvedere Castle" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/belvedere-castle.html">Belvedere Castle</a>, the <a title="Central Park Carousel" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/carousel.html">Central Park Carousel</a>, <a title="Central Park Conservatory Gardens" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/conservatory-garden.html">Conservatory Gardens</a>, and <a title="Central Park Zoo" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/central-park-zoo.html">the Central Park Zoo</a>. Enjoy a picnic at <a title="Sheep Meadow" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/sheep-meadow.html">Sheep Meadow</a> or <a title="the Great Lawn" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/great-lawn.html">the Great Lawn</a>. Watch some baseball at <a title="North Meadow" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/north-meadow.html">North Meadow</a>,&nbsp;go for a run or bike along the Park Drives or <a title="the Reservoir" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/reservoir.html">the Reservoir</a>. For a relaxing day on the water, you can also navigate a rowboat or take a gondola ride across Central Park''s 22-acre <a title="Lake" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/lake.html">Lake</a>.</p>\r\n<table style="background: #ffffff; margin: 5px 0 5px 5px;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #ffffff; width: 200px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/hotels/hotels-rockefeller.jpg" border="0" alt="Rockefeller Center" width="200" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: xx-small;" align="right"><strong>Rockefeller Center</strong> by <em><a onclick="target=''_blank''" href="http://commons.wikimedia.org">Wikimedia Commons</a></em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>If you need directions, check out our&nbsp;<a title="Central Park map" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/maps/poster-maps.html">Central Park map</a> to help you navigate all of its 843 acres.</p>\r\n<table style="background: #ffffff; margin: 5px 0 5px 5px;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<table style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #ffffff; width: 200px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/hotels/hotels-carnegie.jpg" border="0" alt="Carnegie Hall" width="200" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: xx-small;" align="right"><strong>Carnegie Hall</strong> by <em><a onclick="target=''_blank''" href="http://www.dutchperformingarts.com">Dutch Performing Arts</a></em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Central Park hotels are steps away from New York City''s most famous attractions, including Rockefeller Center, Carnegie Hall, and Radio City Music Hall. The Broadway Theater District is close by as well. Enjoy shopping on Fifth Avenue and take in exhibits at the Museum of Modern Art, the Museum of Art and Design, <a title="American Museum of Natural History" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/activities/museums/american-museum-of-natural-history.html">American Museum of Natural History</a> and <a title="The Solomon R. Guggenheim Museum" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/activities/museums/guggenheim-museum.html">The Solomon R. Guggenheim Museum</a>. All are within walking distance to the Park or a subway ride away.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you are coming to the city for art, culture, shopping, dining, <a title="Central Park Tours" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/tours.html">Tours of Central Park</a>&nbsp;or <a title="New York Sightseeing Tours" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/tours/sightseeing.html">New York Sightseeing Tours</a>, you will find it all conveniently located nearby our hotel partners. You can enjoy all the city has to offer with <a onclick="this.target=''_blank'';" rel="nofollow" href="http://www.kqzyfj.com/click-3631793-9707647">The New York Pass - featuring admission to 60 of New York City''s top attractions, starting at only $80 per day!</a></p>\r\n<p>During your stay you''ll also want to check out our list of <a title="Restaurants in Central Park" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/activities/dining-in-the-park.html">restaurants in Central Park</a> as well as our list of <a title="Restaurants around Central Park" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/activities/dining-around-the-park.html">restaurants around Central Park</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style="width: 400px;" border="0" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="4" align="center" bgcolor="#e4cc92">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; color: #000000" colspan="2">CentralPark.com highly recommends: <br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><a href="http://www.marriott.com/hotels/travel/nycex-jw-marriott-essex-house-new-york/" target="_blank"> <img style="margin: 10px 0 0;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/jw-marriott-logo.gif" border="0" alt="The Jumeirah Essex House Hotel" width="158" align="middle" /> </a></td>\r\n<td align="left">\r\n<p><span>A luxurious, stylish and elegant hotel built in 1931. The&nbsp;</span><span>JW Marriott Essex House</span> <span>&nbsp;is quintessentially New York, and it is perfectly located at Central Park. <a href="http://www.marriott.com/hotels/travel/nycex-jw-marriott-essex-house-new-york/" target="_blank"><strong>Visit Website</strong></a> </span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Find top Central Park hotel accommodations in New York right next to Central Park.', 'hotels in central park, new york hotels, central park accommodation, central park bed and breakfast, central park b&b, new york accommodation, new york lodging, central park lodging, luxury hotel central park, place to stay new york, place to stay central park', 4.90, 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Hotels', 'Hotels', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
