(293, '2009-05-19', 98, 2, 14, 'Joe''s Pub in the Park', '', 'activities/shakespeare-in-the-park/joe-s-pub-in-the-park', 'Joe''s Pub in the Park', '<p class="style2"><span class="style8"><span style="color: #000000;"><span class="style9"><strong><img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/graphics/joespub.gif" border="0" alt="Joe''s Pub in the Park" hspace="5" vspace="5" width="199" height="474" align="right" /></strong> </span>A two-week series of paid and FREE  concerts</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="style12"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong><span class="style2"><span class="style8"><span style="color: #000000;">All performances begin at 7PM and presented at The Delacorte  Theater in Central Park</span></span></span></strong><span style="color: #000000;"> (accessible at  81 St. and Central Park West or 79th St.and  5th  Ave)</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="style12"><span class="style13"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #000000;"><a href="http://www.joespub.com/component/option,com_shows/Itemid,40/" target="_blank">CLICK HERE</a> TO VIEW A  COMPLETE SCHEDULE OF SHOWS</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="style12"><span class="style12"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #000000;">Returning for the first  time since it was initially staged in 2004, <strong>JOE&rsquo;S PUB IN THE  PARK</strong> captures the quality and range of performances that have made  Joe&rsquo;s Pub, now in its ninth year of providing music at its downtown home, one of  the most acclaimed and popular clubs in New York City.&nbsp; Pub in the Park brings  that talent and diversity into The Public Theater&rsquo;s most visible and accessible  venue, the annual home of Shakespeare in the Park.&nbsp; Drawing from a pool of the  literally thousands of artists that have performed at Joe&rsquo;s Pub, the event&rsquo;s  programming combines musicians from varying genres and backgrounds together onto  multiple full-length artist bills 