(301, '2011-09-20', 295, 3, 0, 'Download Audio', '', 'tours/walking/self-guided/download-audio', 'Download Central Park Walking Tours Podcasts', '<div class="toursContainer">\r\n<div class="toCenter margin12"><img title="Walking Tours brought to you by Jumeirah and CentralPark.com" usemap="#wt" src="http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?bannerid=154" border="0" alt="Walking Tours brought to you by Jumeirah and CentralPark.com" width="307" height="63" /> \r\n<map name="wt">\r\n<area shape="rect" coords="240,0,307,63" href="http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?bannerid=154" alt="Jumeirah Essex House" target="_blank"></area> \r\n</map>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="separator">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="margin10" style="padding: 0pt 10px; line-height: 16px;">\r\n<p>CentralPark.com Members can download the Central Park Audio Tours by clicking one of the two buttons below.   							After clicking on either of the download buttons just follow the directions that appear in the file download popup.  							(If you''re not a member click <a href="/members/join/">here</a>, registration is quick, painless and free).</p>\r\n<p>After downloading the compressed files click on the icon to unzip the folder holding the mp3 files.   							(If you need to download the WinZip program to decompress the files click <a rel="noindex nofollow" href="http://www.winzip.com/downwz.htm" target="_blank">here</a>)   							Once you have unzipped the files you can upload them to your Ipod using Itunes,  							or transfer the files to another mp3 device.   							And - even if you are nowhere near the park you can download the files and follow the tour on  							the interactive tour maps (<a href="page.php?pid=300">Family</a>, <a href="page.php?pid=299">Arts and Architecture</a>)&nbsp; provided on the site, and take a virtual trip around the heart of New York City.</p>\r\n<p>The Walking Tour audio files are designed to be used in conjunction with the <a href="page.php?pid=304">Wal