(395, '2013-08-19', 145, 2, 15, 'Sharon Bushman', '', 'about-centralpark-com/staff/sharon-bushman', 'Sharon Bushman - CentralPark.com Staff', '<p>Sharon uses her unique photographic talents to capture Central Park weddings and proposals<img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/about/sharon_bushman1.jpg" border="0" alt="" hspace="3" vspace="3" width="250" height="206" align="right" /> for CentralPark.com.&nbsp; Originally from Livonia, Michigan, She graduated from Western Michigan University with a theatre degree. Sharon then moved across the Atlantic and made London, England her home. While there, she attended Mountview Theatre School and lived the life of a struggling actress. After 7 wonderful years, it was time to return to the States and try her luck in the Big Apple. <br /><br />{{ADSPACE_300_250}}<br /><br />Well, life happens, priorities change, and Sharon discovered a tremendous passion for photography.  Capturing people''s emotions in a photograph is such a great joy for her.  It is Sharon''s great pleasure and honor to be able to share that special day with the couple and their loved ones.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You can view Sharon''s work <a href="http://www.sharonbushman.com" target="_blank">here</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Email: sbphotos at yahoo.com</p>', 'CentralPark.com -  Your first stop for information on Central Park, New York City and The Central Park Zoo, 830 5th Ave. New York, NY 1002. Including extensive event listings, maps, attractions, sports, activities, history, essential info for tourists.', 'Central Park, Central Park Zoo, NYC, New York City, Belvedere Castle, Bethesda Fountain, Bethesda Terrace, Bow Bridge, Central Park Maps, Great Lawn, reservoir, running track, Sheep Meadow, Strawberry Fields, Tavern on the Green, tours, walking tours, Wollman Rink', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', 'belvedere.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Sharon Bushman', 'Sharon Bushman', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
