(424, '2011-10-03', 145, 2, 15, 'Eileen Callen', '', 'about-centralpark-com/staff/eileen-callen', 'Eileen Callen - Central Park Staff | Your Complete Guide at CentralPark.com', '<p><img style="float: right;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/eileen.jpg" alt="Eileen" hspace="5" vspace="5" width="188" height="252" /></p>\r\n<p>Eileen Callen is the Marketing Director of CentralPark.com. During her time in New York she has developed online marketing strategies and custom programs for clients across all industries.&nbsp;She brings this experience to CentralPark.com to help grow the site and ensure its continued success as a useful destination for Central Park lovers and visitors from all over the world.</p>\r\n<p>Central Park has always been a place of great memories for Eileen, whether for hiking, reading a book, sipping on hot cocoa, watching the ducks, or just sharing a blanket with good friends.</p>', 'CentralPark.com -  Your first stop for information on Central Park, New York City and The Central Park Zoo, 830 5th Ave. New York, NY 10021. Including extensive event listings, maps, attractions, sports, activities, history, essential info for tourists.', 'Central Park, Central Park Zoo, NYC, New York City, Belvedere Castle, Bethesda Fountain, ice skating, Bow Bridge, Central Park Maps, Great Lawn, reservoir, running track, Sheep Meadow, Strawberry Fields, Tavern on the Green, tours, walking tours, Wollman Rink', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', 'sheep_meadow.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Eileen Callen', 'Eileen Callen', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
