(441, '2010-07-15', 326, 1, 14, 'Spring 2010 Winners', '', 'photo-contest/spring-2010-contest-winners', 'Spring 2010 Photo Contest Finalists', '<div id="photosContainer">\r\n<div class="no-overflow">\r\n<div class="logoContainer"><a title="CentralPark.com Photo Contest" href="page.php?pid=326"><img title="CentralPark.com Photo Contest" src="/img/photos/contest.main.cp.gif" alt="CentralPark.com Photo Contest - brought to you by Jumeirah Essex House" width="182" height="38" /></a></div>\r\n<h1 class="greenTitle">Winners of the Spring 2010 Photo Contest</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>As the flowers bloomed in Central Park this spring so did the work of the 104 photographers who submitted their pictures in the Spring 2010 Photo Contest.  		The entries were florally inspired and conveyed the vast beauty of the Park with portraits of friendly animals, scenic landscapes, budding flowers and other spring-themed photos.  		As always, with such a fantastic pool of work to choose from, the judges had their hands full.  		After your votes narrowed the field down to the 30 Finalist, the panel carefully deliberated and selected the final winners.  		In fact, the photos were so inspired that there was a two-way tie for the honor of 3rd place photo.</p>\r\n<div class="separator">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3 style="margin: 15px 0pt 8px;"><img title="1st Place" src="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-spring-2010/title.1st.place.jpg" alt="1st Place" width="135" height="33" /></h3>\r\n<div><a title="Pink Romance" rel="lightboxspring" href="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-spring-2010/large.1st.place.jpg" target="_blank"><img style="border: 1px solid #cccccc;" title="Pink Romance" src="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-spring-2010/thumb.1st.place.jpg" alt="Pink Romance" width="400" /></a>\r\n<div>Pink Romance,<br /> by <strong><a title="View profile" href="http://www.centralpark.com/members/profile34332.html">starshine2266</a></strong></div>\r\n<p>A couple strolls hand-in-hand in Central Park</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="separator">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3 style="margin: 15px 0pt 8px;"><img title="2nd Place" src="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-spring-2010/title.2nd.place.jpg" alt="2nd Place" width="100" height="24" /></h3>\r\n<div><a title="Central Park In Spring, plain and simple.." rel="lightboxspring" href="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-spring-2010/large.2nd.place.jpg" target="_blank"><img style="border: 1px solid #cccccc;" title="Central Park In Spring, plain and simple.." src="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-spring-2010/thumb.2nd.place.jpg" alt="Central Park In Spring, plain and simple.." width="400" /></a>\r\n<div>Central Park In Spring, plain and simple..<br /> by <strong><a title="View profile" href="http://www.centralpark.com/members/profile5966.html">Philip</a></strong></div>\r\n<p>The effect that N.Y''s CP has on people; the park is the life blood of NYC. There is no ducking here, no discount deal, no short cut, your thoughts are primed and sharpened, especially in the spring, for the sun rejuvenates you.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="separator">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3 style="margin: 15px 0pt 8px;"><img title="3rd Place" src="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-spring-2010/title.3rd.place.jpg" alt="3rd Place" width="163" height="24" /></h3>\r\n<table style="width: 400px;" border="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td style="padding: 0 7px 15px 0;"><a title="Down to drink." rel="lightboxspring" href="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-spring-2010/large.3rd.place.1.jpg" target="_blank"><img style="border: 1px solid #cccccc;" title="Down to drink." src="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-spring-2010/thumb.3rd.place.1.jpg" alt="Down to drink." width="200" /></a>\r\n<div>Down to drink.,<br /> by <strong><a title="View profile" href="http://www.centralpark.com/members/profile34165.html">cmolina31</a></strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>Red Tail Hawk</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td style="padding: 0 7px 15px 0;"><a title="Zoo Dude" rel="lightboxspring" href="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-spring-2010/large.3rd.place.2.jpg" target="_blank"><img style="border: 1px solid #cccccc;" title="Zoo Dude" src="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-spring-2010/thumb.3rd.place.2.jpg" alt="Zoo Dude" width="200" /></a>\r\n<div>Zoo Dude,<br /> by <strong><a title="View profile" href="http://www.centralpark.com/members/profile25071.html">geckoess</a></strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>Tropical bird in Central Park Zoo Tropical.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class="separator">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br /> \r\n<ul class="green">\r\n<li> <a title="Enter in the CentralPark.com Photo Contest" href="/members/photos/add/step-1">Enter Now!</a> </li>\r\n<li class="last"> <a title="Rate contest photos" href="/photos/contest/all">Rate Photos</a> </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Here''s the winners of the 2010 Spring Photo Contest.', 'photo contest finalists, spring contest finalists, central park photos, photo contest, grand prize, spring photo contest', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', 'belvedere.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '/usr/media/contest/contest.css,/css/slimbox/slimbox.css', '/usr/media/contest/slimbox-original.js', 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Spring 2010 Winners', 'Spring 2010 Winners', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(442, '2015-04-24', 0, 0, 3, 'Central Park and New York Tours', '', 'tours', 'Central Park Tours', '<div id="toursWrapper">\r\n<h1 class="mainTour title">Central Park and New York Tours</h1>\r\n<p><strong> Tour Central Park on your own or with a licensed expert! Many of our guided tours are offered in English, Spanish, Portuguese, German, Dutch, Italian, Turkish and Russian.</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="toursList">\r\n<li class="hcr"> <a href="/guide/tours/horse-carriage-tours.html"> Horse &amp; Carriage Tours <span>The classic way to see Central Park</span> </a> </li>\r\n<li class="bike"> <a href="/guide/tours/bike-rentals.html"> Bike Rentals <span>Cruise the park at your leisure</span> </a> </li>\r\n<li class="bike"> <a href="/guide/tours/bike.html"> Bike Tours <span>Be accompanied by a knowledgeable guide</span> </a> </li>\r\n<!--\r\n<li class="vespa"> <a href="/guide/tours/vespa.html" mce_href="/guide/tours/vespa.html"> Vespa Tours 	<span>Zip around Central Park and NYC on a scooter tour</span> </a> </li>\r\n-->\r\n<li class="walking"> <a href="/guide/tours/walking.html"> Walking Tours 	<span>See Central Park and more on foot</span> </a> </li>\r\n<li class="pedicab"> <a href="/guide/tours/pedicab.html"> Pedicab Tours <span>The ideal choice to sit back and enjoy the scenery</span> </a> </li>\r\n<li class="nyc"> <a href="/guide/tours/sightseeing.html"> NYC Tours 	<span>Want to see even more of New York City?</span> </a> </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><img title="Central Park and NYC Tours" src="/usr/media/tours.v2/tour-photos.jpg" alt="Central Park and NYC Tours" width="400" height="66" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>', 'Explore Central Park and all of its beauty with a bike rental, bike tour, walking tour, horse & carriage ride, vespa tour, or a pedicab tour. Licensed and knowledgeable tour guides! Tours in English, Spanish, Portuguese, German, Dutch, Russian, Italian, Turkish and Russian available. Book a tour on CentralPark.com.', 'central park tour, walking tour, bike tour, bicycle tour, pedicab tour, self-guided tour, tour of central park, visit central park, multi-lingual tours, bilingual tours, tours in spanish, tours in portuguese, tours in german, tours in dutch, tours in russian, tours in italian, tours in turkish, central park movie tour, central park arts and architecture tour', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', 'bethesda.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '/usr/media/tours.v2/tours.css', '', 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Tours', 'Tours', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(443, '2015-07-29', 442, 1, 7, 'Bike Tours', '', 'tours/bike', 'Central Park Bike Tours', '<div id="toursWrapper">\r\n<h1 class="bikeTour title">Bike Tours</h1>\r\n<div id="toursWrapper"><strong> Have an expert guide you through Central Park on a bike tour! Tours in English, Spanish, German, Dutch and Russian.</strong></div>\r\n<p>Cycle along the scenic paths of Central Park with your bike tour guide and visit many famous landmarks and attractions!</p>\r\n<script src="https://fareharbor.com/embeds/script/calendar-small/smyrnatours/items/1293,1343,1297,1344/?lightframe=yes&amp;asn=centralpark"></script>\r\n<p><strong>Bike pickup</strong> is located at 208 W. 80th Street, New York, NY 10024</p>\r\n<p>We have over 400 bikes for your bike tour ranging in styles and sizes from&nbsp;14" kids bikes to 26" adult bikes, leisure bikes, comfort bikes, road bikes, mountain bikes, and we also carry tandem bikes, baby seats and baby trailers. Delivery is also available anywhere between 42nd street and 72nd street (minimums may apply).</p>\r\nWe include a helmet, basket, lock and map at no extra charge. We have over 400 bikes for men, women and kids as well as tandem bike rentals, baby seats and baby trailers. <br /> <br />\r\n<div class="included"><span>We include a helmet, basket, lock and map at no extra charge. We have over 400 bikes for men, women and kids as well as tandem bike rentals, baby seats and baby trailers.</span></div>\r\n<p>Please&nbsp;<a title="centralpark.com contact us" href="http://www.centralpark.com/contact">contact us</a> with any questions.</p>\r\n<div><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;">{{ADSPACE_300_250}}</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 25px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3 id="t1">ARTS &amp; ARCHITECTURE TOUR &mdash; 1 hour</h3>\r\n<p>The Arts and Architecture tour is a great way to learn about the major attractions and features that make Central Park the amazing and inspirational place that it is. This tour can last for one or two hours:</p>\r\n<p><strong>The 1-hour tour covers the following stops along the way:</strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Balto</li>\r\n<li>Bandshell</li>\r\n<li>Bethesda Terrace</li>\r\n<li>Bethesda Fountain</li>\r\n<li>Carousel</li>\r\n<li>Cherry Hill</li>\r\n<li>Children''s Zoo</li>\r\n<li>Dairy</li>\r\n<li>Dakota</li>\r\n<li>Essex House</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Grand Army Plaza</li>\r\n<li>Heckscher Playground</li>\r\n<li>The Lake</li>\r\n<li>The Mall</li>\r\n<li>Sheep Meadow</li>\r\n<li>Strawberry Fields</li>\r\n<li>SummerStage</li>\r\n<li>Tavern on the Green</li>\r\n<li>Victorian Gardens</li>\r\n<li>Wollman Rink</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class="sep">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>ARTS &amp; ARCHITECTURE TOUR &mdash; 2 hours</h3>\r\n<p><strong>The 2-hour tour covers everything from the 1-hour tour, plus:</strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Belvedere Castle</li>\r\n<li>Conservatory Garden</li>\r\n<li>Conservatory Water</li>\r\n<li>Delacorte Music Clock</li>\r\n<li>Delacorte Theater</li>\r\n<li>Gapstow Bridge</li>\r\n<li>Greyshot Arch</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Heckscher Ballfields</li>\r\n<li>Loeb Boathouse</li>\r\n<li>Reservoir</li>\r\n<li>Shakespeare Garden</li>\r\n<li>Swedish Cottage</li>\r\n<li>Turtle Pond</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class="sep">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3 id="t2">MOVIE &amp; TV SITES TOUR &mdash; 1 hour</h3>\r\n<p>Learn how Central Park was made famous in the movies and on TV on this exciting tour that will take you to the sites of many well-known TV and movie scenes. This tour can last for one or two hours:</p>\r\n<p><strong>The 1-hour tour covers the following movies and TV shows:</strong></p>\r\n<table style="wid