(447, '2015-07-06', 442, 1, 1, 'Walking Tours', '', 'tours/walking', 'Central Park Walking Tours', '<div id="toursWrapper">\r\n<h1 class="walkingTour title">Walking Tours</h1>\r\n<p><strong> Take a guided Central Park walking tour with a licensed expert! Many of our tours are offered in English, Spanish, Portuguese, German, Dutch, Italian, Turkish and Russian.</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="toursList wtList">\r\n<li class="wt-aa">\r\n<h2><a href="/guide/tours/walking/arts-architecture-tours.html">Arts and Architecture Tour</a></h2>\r\n<p>What makes Central Park so special and inspiring? See attractions such as Belvedere Castle, Conservatory Garden, Gapstow Bridge, Shakespeare Garden, the Loeb Boathouse and more.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class="wt-tv">\r\n<h2><a href="/guide/tours/walking/movie-tv-sites-tours.html">Movie &amp; TV Sites Tour</a></h2>\r\n<p>Experience a piece of Hollywood in Central Park and see where many famous movie &amp; tv scenes were shot, for example: Ghostbusters, Home Alone 2, Spiderman 3, Maid in Manhattan, Enchanted, Friends, Sex in the City, Saturday Night Live, Gossip Girl, 30 Rock and many more.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class="wt-hs">\r\n<h2><a href="/guide/tours/walking/hidden-secrets-tour.html">Hidden Secrets Tour</a></h2>\r\n<p>Explore the paths less traveled in Central Park and discover its hidden gems! This exciting 3-hour walking tour will lead you through the woods to some unique destinations uncovered by most other tours. The tour includes a stop for coffee or a snack plus a surprise bonus at the end.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<h2><a title="Citifari Central Park Photo Tour" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/tours/walking/citifari.html">Citifari Photo Walking Tour</a></h2>\r\n<p>Learn how to capture some of Central Park''s most beautiful lakes, bridges and attractions, as well as the skyline of Manhattan.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class="wt-holiday">\r\n<h2><a href="/guide/tours/walking-tours/holiday-sights-tour.html">Holiday Sights Tour</a></h2>\r\n<p>From Nov 15th to Jan 5th. New York has beautiful sights to see during the holidays, so get your cameras ready and get in the holiday spirit on this fun and festive walking tour covering Central Park, Rockefeller Center and more.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<script type="text/javascript"><!--\r\n		window.addEvent(''load'', function() { \r\n			$$(''.wtList li'').addEvent(''click'', function() { \r\n				document.location = this.getElementsBySelector(''a'')[0].href; \r\n			}); \r\n		});\r\n// --></script>\r\n</div>', 'Take a guided walking tour of Central Park and discover what makes it so special through art, architecture, history, movies, tv and more. Your tour guide can also show you the hidden gems of the park that are unexplored by most.', '', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', 'bethesda.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 7, '/usr/media/tours.v2/tours.css', '/usr/media/tours.v2/tours.js', 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Walking Tours', 'Walking Tours', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(448, '2012-11-15', 447, 2, 6, 'Guided Walking Tours', '', 'tours/walking/guided', 'Central Park Guided Walking Tours', '<div id="toursWrapper">\r\n<h1 class="walkingTour title">Walking Tours</h1>\r\n<div id="toursWrapper"><strong> Have an expert lead you through Central Park on a walking tour!</strong></div>\r\n<div><strong><br /></strong></div>\r\n<table style="width: 400px;" border="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 48%; padding-right: 2%;">\r\n<p>Choose from two types of guided walking tours - the <a href="#aa">Arts &amp; Architecture Tour</a> or the <a href="#tv">Movie &amp; TV Sites</a> tour.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class="alignR valignTop" style="width: 50%;"><a href="/tours/walking-tour"><img src="/usr/media/tours.v2/reserve-online-walking.png" alt="Reserve Online" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12px;"><a href="/tours/walking-tour?duration=1"><strong>1 and 2 Hours Tours</strong></a></span></p>\r\n<p>Offered daily at 9:00 am, 12:00 noon, 3:00 pm and 5:00 pm. Available every hour on the hour for groups of 4 or more. Depending on your walking speed, the 2 hour tour covers about one half of the park (choose from <a href="#aa-nc">North Center</a> and <a href="#aa-sc">South Center</a> tours) in approximately 2 to 2 1/2 hours.</p>\r\n<br /><big><a href="/tours/walking-tour?duration=2"><strong>5 Hours Tour</strong></a></big>\r\n<p>Offered daily at 9:00 am and 3:00 pm. The 5 hour tour includes everything from the 2 hour tour plus a visit the Central Park Carousel. You also get to choose between a visit the Central Park Zoo or a picnic lunch.</p>\r\n<br /><big><a href="/tours/walking-tour?customtour=1"><strong>Custom Tour</strong></a></big>\r\n<p>You can also request a custom tour with us. Please specify what you are looking for in the comments section of the reservation form and we will be happy to work with you. Pricing for custom tours will vary on time and locations wanted.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<table clas