er Ballfields</li>\r\n<li>Loeb Boathouse</li>\r\n<li>Reservoir</li>\r\n<li>Shakespeare Garden</li>\r\n<li>Swedish Cottage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<p id="aa-sc"><strong>SOUTH-CENTER TOUR</strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Balto</li>\r\n<li>Bandshell</li>\r\n<li>Bethesda Terrace</li>\r\n<li>Bethesda Fountain</li>\r\n<li>Carousel</li>\r\n<li>Cherry Hill</li>\r\n<li>Children''s Zoo</li>\r\n<li>Dairy</li>\r\n<li>Dakota</li>\r\n<li>Essex House</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Grand Army Plaza</li>\r\n<li>Heckscher Playground</li>\r\n<li>The Lake</li>\r\n<li>The Mall</li>\r\n<li>Sheep Meadow</li>\r\n<li>Strawberry Fields</li>\r\n<li>SummerStage</li>\r\n<li>Tavern on the Green</li>\r\n<li>Victorian Gardens</li>\r\n<li>Wollman Rink</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class="sep"><a href="#toursWrapper">Back to top &uarr;</a></div>\r\n<h3 id="tv">MOVIE &amp; TV SITES TOUR</h3>\r\n<p>Experience a piece of Hollywood in Central Park.</p>\r\n<p id="tv-nc"><strong>NORTH-CENTER TOUR</strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Gossip Girl</li>\r\n<li>Saturday Night Live</li>\r\n<li>Sex in the City</li>\r\n<li>Friends</li>\r\n<li>30 Rock</li>\r\n<li>Sesame Street</li>\r\n<li>Elimidate</li>\r\n<li>Six Degrees</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Kidnapped</li>\r\n<li>The Apprentice</li>\r\n<li>Project Runway</li>\r\n<li>The Food Network</li>\r\n<li>Queer Eye for the Straight Guy</li>\r\n<li>Discovery</li>\r\n<li>Animal Planet</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<p id="tv-nc"><strong>SOUTH-CENTER TOUR</strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Bo