(450, '2010-12-22', 442, 1, 14, 'Private NYC Tours', '', 'tours/private-nyc-tours', 'Private NYC Tours', '<table border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right" bgcolor="#ffffff">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img style="border: 0pt none;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/mkot.1.jpg" alt="Times Square at Night" width="200" height="131" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img style="border: 0pt none;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/mkot.2.jpg" alt="Mid Town 59th Street" width="200" height="131" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img style="border: 0pt none;" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/mkot.3.jpg" alt="Guggenheim" width="200" height="131" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Take a private, personalized tour with My Kind of Town New York, <strong>voted "Best Private Tour Company in New York" in 2010</strong> by the New York Association of Hotel Concierges.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Tour Services Include:</p>\r\n<ul class="bullet">\r\n<li>Private, personalized tour in a luxury Mercedes Benz SUV&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Knowledgeable, entertaining &amp; licensed tour guides</li>\r\n<li>Tours of New York City neighborhoods, eateries, shopping, wine tasting or create your own personal tour</li>\r\n<li>Pick-up and drop-off services at your hotel, coffee shop, restaurant, etc.</li>\r\n<li>Assistance with lunch and dinner reservations at local restaurants</li>\r\n<li>Accommodations for special needs/physically challenged guests</li>\r\n<li>Foreign language tours can also be arranged</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Advanced reservations are required.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Request more information directly through our <a href="/forms/private-nyc-tours">online form</a>:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="center"><a style="background: none;" href="/forms/private-nyc-tours"><img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/mkot.button.gif" alt="Online Reservation Inquiry Form" width="202" height="57" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Be sure to mention that you heard about My Kind of Town on CentralPark.com, and&nbsp;don''t forget to ask about the Christmas Light Tour!</p>\r\n<p><strong>Additional Contact Info:<br /></strong>(212) 754-4500<br />(866) 691-8687 (toll free)<br /><a href="mailto:info@mykindoftown.com" target="_blank">info@mykindoftown.com</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', 'water.jpg', '<a href="http://www.luminous-newyork.com">Joergen Geerds</a>', '', '', 1, '', '', 0, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Private NYC Tours', 'Private NYC Tours', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(451, '2010-10-28', 326, 1, 14, 'Summer 2010 Winners', '', 'photo-contest/summer-2010-winners', 'Summer 2010 Photo Contest Winners', '<div id="photosContainer">\r\n<div class="no-overflow">\r\n<div class="logoContainer"><a title="CentralPark.com Photo Contest" href="page.php?pid=326"><img title="CentralPark.com Photo Contest" src="/img/photos/contest.main.cp.gif" alt="CentralPark.com Photo Contest - brought to you by Jumeirah Essex House" width="182" height="38" /></a></div>\r\n<h1 class="greenTitle">Winners of the Summer 2010 Photo Contest</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>The 2010 Summer Photo Contest had some of the most beautiful entries yet, which included portraits of friendly animals, scenic landscapes and flowers in full bloom. As always, with such a fantastic pool of work to choose from, the judges had their hands full. After your votes narrowed the field down to the 30 finalists, the panel carefully deliberated and selected the final winners.</p>\r\n<div class="separator">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3 style="margin: 15px 0pt 8px;"><img title="1st Place" src="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-summer-2010/title.1st.place.jpg" alt="1st Place" width="135" height="33" /></h3>\r\n<div><a title="Bethesda Fountain" rel="lightboxsummer" href="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-summer-2010/large.1st.place.jpg" target="_blank"><img style="border: 1px solid #cccccc;" title="Bethesda Fountain" src="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-summer-2010/large.1st.place.jpg" alt="Bethesda Fountain" width="400" /></a>\r\n<div>Bethesda Fountain, by <strong><a title="View profile" href="http://www.centralpark.com/members/profile2522.html">eddtoro35</a></strong></div>\r\n<p>View of teh Bethesda Fountain and terrace on a summer evening.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="separator">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3 style="margin: 15px 0pt 8px;"><img title="2nd Place" src="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-summer-2010/title.2nd.place.jpg" alt="2nd Place" width="100" height="24" /></h3>\r\n<div><a title="Monarch Butterfly" rel="lightboxsummer" href="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-summer-2010/large.2nd.place.jpg" target="_blank"><img style="border: 1px solid #cccccc;" title="Monarch Butterfly" src="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-summer-2010/large.2nd.place.jpg" alt="Monarch Butterfly" width="400" /></a>\r\n<div>Monarch Butterfly, by <strong><a title="View profile" href="http://www.centralpark.com/members/profile37834.html">ejyang06</a></strong></div>\r\n<p>Monarch Butterfly (Danaus plexippus) is one of the most stunning creatures in North America. This Monarch buttefly is resting in Central Park, getting ready for its journey to Mexico.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="separator">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3 style="margin: 15px 0pt 8px;"><img title="3rd Place" src="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-summer-2010/title.3rd.place.jpg" alt="3rd Place" width="163" height="24" /></h3>\r\n<div><a title="Gapstow goes Green" rel="lightboxsummer" href="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-summer-2010/large.3rd.place.jpg" target="_blank"><img style="border: 1px solid #cccccc;" title="Gapstow goes Green" src="http://www.centralpark.com/usr/media/contest/winners-summer-2010/large.3rd.place.jpg" alt="Gapstow goes Green" width="400" /></a>\r\n<div>Gapstow goes Green, by <strong><a title="View profile" href="http://www.centralpark.com/members/profile19181.html">scholl10</a></strong></div>\r\n<p>What''s not to like about Gapstow?</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="separator">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br /> \r\n<ul class="green">\r\n<li class="last"> <a title="Rate contest photos" href="/photos/contest/all">Rate Photos</a> </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Here are the winners of the 2010 Summer Photo Contest.', 'photo contest winners, spring contest finalists, central park photos, photo contest, grand prize, spring photo contest', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', 'belvedere.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '/usr/media/contest/contest.css,/css/slimbox/slimbox.css', '/usr/media/contest/slimbox-original.js', 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Summer 2010 Winners', 'Summer 2010 Winners', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(452, '2014-11-06', 0, 0, 15, 'Special Events', '', 'special-events', 'Central Park Special Events', '<div id="spEventsWrapper">\r\n<h1 class="mainSpEvents title">Special Events</h1>\r\n<p>Our event team can help you with planning all of your special events, including private and corporate outings, big group tours and picnics, intimate gatherings, class reunions, bachelor and bachelorette parties, and parties for kids from 25 to 1000 guests.</p>\r\n<p class="alignC"><a class="noHoverBg" href="http://www.centralpark.com/forms/special-events"><img src="/usr/media/btn.contact-us.png" alt="Contact Us" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul class="eventsList">\r\n<li class="pce"><strong>PRIVATE &amp; CORPORATE EVENTS </strong>\r\n<p>Inspire &amp; value your work team, international clients, or private group party by treating them to some outdoor fun in the park. We can help you create the perfect package from lakeside picnics to softball games, teambuilding events, bachelor/bachelorette parties and more.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class="cptp"><strong>CENTRAL PARK TOURS &amp; PICNICS </strong>\r\n<p>Enjoy all the beauty that Central Park has to offer and explore this urban oasis with a guided tour and picnic! We can help you put together packages for guided walking tours, bike tours, pedicab rides, horse &amp; carriage rides, and picnic gatherings.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class="cp"><strong>CHILDREN''S PARTIES </strong>\r\n<p>Create the perfect party for kids of all ages, from face painting to clowns to scavenger hunts and zoo animal fun. We''ll help you create a day they''re sure to remember!</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Your one-stop Central Park event planning team offering all-inclusive special events, corporate outings, bachelor and bachelorette parties, class reunions, private and intimate gatherings, and parties for kids from 25 to 1000 guests.', 'special events, birthdays, anniversaries, walking tours, picnics, corporate outings, reunions, office parties, kids parties, all-inclusive, private events, private parties, children''s parties, kid''s parties, bachelor parties, bachelorette parties, class reunions, holiday parties', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '/usr/media/special-events/style.css', '', 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Special Events', 'Special Events', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
