(463, '2015-04-27', 442, 1, 15, 'Horse & Carriage Tours', '', 'tours/horse-carriage-tours', 'Central Park Horse & Carriage Tour Reservations', '<div id="toursWrapper">\r\n<h1 class="horseCarriageTour title">Horse &amp; Carriage Tours</h1>\r\n<ul class="hc-carousel">\r\n<li style="display: block;"> <a title="Horse and Carriage Tours" rel="lightbox-guide" href="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/horse___carriage/horse-carriage-01.jpg"> <img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/horse___carriage/thumb-horse-carriage-01.jpg" alt="Horse and Carriage Tours" width="400" /> </a> </li>\r\n<li style="display: none;"> <a title="Horse and Carriage Tours" rel="lightbox-guide" href="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/horse___carriage/horse-carriage-02.jpg"> <img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/horse___carriage/thumb-horse-carriage-02.jpg" alt="Horse and Carriage Tours" width="400" /> </a> </li>\r\n<li style="display: none;"> <a title="Horse and Carriage Tours" rel="lightbox-guide" href="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/horse___carriage/horse-carriage-03.jpg"> <img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/horse___carriage/thumb-horse-carriage-03.jpg" alt="Horse and Carriage Tours" width="400" /> </a> </li>\r\n<li style="display: none;"> <a title="Horse and Carriage Tours" rel="lightbox-guide" href="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/horse___carriage/horse-carriage-04.jpg"> <img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/horse___carriage/thumb-horse-carriage-04.jpg" alt="Horse and Carriage Tours" width="400" /> </a> </li>\r\n<li style="display: none;"> <a title="Horse and Carriage Tours" rel="lightbox-guide" href="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/horse___carriage/horse-carriage-05.jpg"> <img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/horse___carriage/thumb-horse-carriage-05.jpg" alt="Horse and Carriage Tours" width="400" /> </a> </li>\r\n<li style="display: none;"> <a title="Horse and Carriage Tours" rel="lightbox-guide" href="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/horse___carriage/horse-carriage-06.jpg"> <img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/horse___carriage/thumb-horse-carriage-06.jpg" alt="Horse and Carriage Tours" width="400" /> </a> </li>\r\n<li style="display: none;"> <a title="Horse and Carriage Tours" rel="lightbox-guide" href="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/horse___carriage/horse-carriage-07.jpg"> <img src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/horse___carriage/thumb-horse-carriage-07.jpg" alt="Horse and Carriage Tours" width="400" /> </a> </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<p><strong>Our most popular tour of Central Park!</strong></p>\r\n<div id="toursWrapper">Customized rides for weddings, proposals, birthdays, anniversaries, and other special occassions. Add photography, flowers, chocolates, special requests and more.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><strong><br /></strong></p>\r\n<table class="pricing" border="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<thead> \r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="col-1">Customized Horse &amp; Carriage Rides</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead> \r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="col-1">\r\n<p>45 min rides starting at $155</p>\r\n<p><em><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">Choose a date from the calendar below:</span></span></em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br /> <br />\r\n<script src="https://fareharbor.com/embeds/script/calendar-small/smyrnatours/items/1256/?lightframe=yes&amp;asn=centralpark"></script>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong><strong>Meet your driver at</strong><strong>&nbsp;<a title="horse and carriage meeting point" href="https://goo.gl/maps/VcCix" target="_blank">Columbus Circle</a>&nbsp;</strong><strong>in front of FedEx<strong>.</strong></strong></strong></p>\r\n<div><strong><br /></strong></div>\r\n<ul class="hc-testimonials">\r\n<li style="display: block;">\r\n<p><em>Our driver was awesome! He even took a few pictures for us after and let us give his horsie a carrot or two. Please share with him how pleased I was with my ride and I''ll definitely recommend your tours to anyone heading to the area in the future. Thank you again!</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="display: none;">\r\n<p><em>The ride was lovely, the driver accommodating with stops for photos. Would recommend the experience.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="display: none;">\r\n<p><em>Great&hellip;.Our driver was great-very informative and just a relaxing ride.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="display: none;">\r\n<p><em>Very enjoyable, lovely oasis in the middle of the city.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="display: none;">\r\n<p><em>Our driver and photographer were magnificent! They were personable and took the time to get to know what we wanted.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="display: none;">\r\n<p><em>I loved the tour. Our driver was extremely nice and helped make the proposal extremely special.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="display: none;">\r\n<p><em>Amazing - our driver and horse were fantastic. So much knowledge of the park and such a pleasure. The horse was so soft and sweet too! We had a great time!!!</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="display: none;">\r\n<p><em>Our driver was AWESOME. Loved his horse and the photographer was AMAZING!</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="display: none;">\r\n<p><em>OUTSTANDING!!!! Our driver was very prompt and kept us informed of his status for meeting up. He was very gracious, took several pictures for us after and even let us give his horse a carrot or two.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="display: none;">\r\n<p><em>Very enjoyable. Our driver gave interesting information as we made our way around the park and was very accommodating.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="display: none;">\r\n<p><em>Fantastic! Driver was so nice &amp; kind. My son asked if he could pet the horse &amp; our driver actually let him feed the horse.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="display: none;">\r\n<p><em>It was fabulous, the driver was extremely friendly and informative, the ride was smooth and he kept the pace just right so that we could see everything we wanted to.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="display: none;">\r\n<p><em>Excellent tour. The guide was informative and very personable. The carriage was clean and very presentable. The horse was well cared for.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class="last" style="display: none;">\r\n<p><em>Our driver was AWESOME!!! What a great personality! His knowledge of all things Central Park was impressive. My wife and I celebrated our 10 year anniversary, and the carriage ride and flowers were so important. I would recommend your website to anyone who would like to do this. Thanks to our super-friendly, smiling driver who hails from Turkey! He was a pleasure to have as part of our very special night.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<script type="text/javascript"><!--\r\ninitHCPage && window.addEvent(''load'', initHCPage);\r\n// --></script>\r\n<p style="font-size: 10px; padding: 2px 0;">Horse-drawn carriages are a unique and historical way to experience the beauty of Central Park. Get a taste of old-time New York on a horse-drawn carriage ride through the winding trails of Central Park.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong><strong></strong>Why book ahead vs. take a walk-up ride?</strong>&nbsp;<em>Pre-arranging guarantees availability and also allows for carriage ride customization.</em></p>\r\n<p><strong>Is there a difference in price?&nbsp;</strong><em>Prices for pre-arranged carriage rides are based on the standard walkup rate (see below) plus an advanced reservation booking fee.&nbsp;</em><em>Walk-up rides without a reservation are $50 for *up to* 20 mins, plus $20 per extra 10 mins, plus tip.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em></em><strong>How many people can ride in one carriage?</strong> <em>One carriage can accommodate up to 4 adults, or 3 adults and 2 small children.</em></p>\r\n<p><strong>Other Notes</strong></p>\r\n<p><em>In the event that the horse &amp; carriage rides are discontinued in Central Park, full refunds will be given.</em></p>\r\n<p><em></em> Call&nbsp;+1 (347) 871-4499&nbsp;to schedule reservations that are within 24 hours.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For marriage proposals:</strong> &nbsp;Please add 15 mins extra if you want to get out of the carriage to propose.</p>\r\n<p>Please remember to tip your driver.</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-style: italic;"> </span></p>\r\n<p><strong>During the Holiday Season (Nov 24 - Jan 5)</strong> and <strong>Valentine''s Day (Feb 14)</strong> <strong>high season prices apply</strong> to pre-arranged Horse &amp; Carriage rides. Walk-up prices stay the same.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cancellation Policy</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Full refund provided with 24 hours cancellation notice. Early same day cancellations will incur a $50 cancellation penalty. No refunds for last hour cancellations. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>**Please be on time** Drivers are unable to accommodate your entire tour if you are late.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="font-size: 10px; padding: 2px 0;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 10px; padding: 2px 0;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/RvXnN64hgIQ" width="400" height="225" frameborder="0"></iframe></div>\r\n<p style="font-size: 10px; padding: 2px 0;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In New York City, horses are a symbol of a bygone era before the advent of cars, buses and trains. It was during this time that New Yorkers got around from place to place on horseback or by means of horse-drawn carriage. As a result and over time, horses became iconic to the history of Manhattan.</p>\r\n</div>', 'Reserve a horse and carriage tour online and experience the beauty of Central Park. Surprise proposals, weddings, anniversaries, birthdays, photography, chocolates, flowers and more. Customized rides for special occasions.', 'horse and carriage rides, horse-drawn carriages, carriage ride, horse and carriage tour, multi-lingual tours, bilingual tours, tours in spanish, tours in portuguese, tours in german, tours in dutch, tours in russian, tours in italian, tours in turkish, horse and buggy ride', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', 'horsebuggy800.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 4, '/usr/media/tours.v2/tours.css', '/usr/media/tours.v2/tours.js', 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Horse & Carriage Tours', 'Horse & Carriage Tours', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(465, '2015-06-23', 442, 1, 15, 'NYC Sightseeing Tours', '', 'tours/sightseeing', 'NYC Sightseeing Tours', '<table style="background: #fff; padding-left: 5px;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img title="Sightseeing" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/sightseeing-1.jpg" alt="Sightseeing" width="160" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img title="Sightseeing" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/sightseeing-2.jpg" alt="Sightseeing" width="160" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img title="Sightseeing" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/sightseeing-3.jpg" alt="Sightseeing" width="160" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img title="Sightseeing" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/tours/sightseeing-4.jpg" alt="Sightseeing" width="160" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Looking for fun and affordable guided tours in New York?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Visit unique attractions, world-famous museums, theaters, skyscrapers and more. Check out bus tours and helicopter tours as well!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Get your cameras ready and learn as you go with <a title="citifari photography tours" href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/classes/citifari.html">Citifari Photography Tours</a></p>\r\n<p>A sightseeing must-have for NYC: <a href="http://www.kqzyfj.com/click-3631793-9707647" target="_top">The New York Pass--Admission to 60 of New York City''s top attractions, starting at $80 per day!</a><img src="http://www.tqlkg.com/image-3631793-9707647" border="0" alt="" width="1" height="1" /></p>\r\n<p>Great deal! <a href="http://www.anrdoezrs.net/click-3631793-10543584" target="_top">Save big on our New York Pass and Double-Decker Bus Tour combo!</a><img src="http://www.awltovhc.com/image-3631793-10543584" border="0" alt="" width="1" height="1" /></p>\r\n<p>Get discounted passes <a href="http://www.tkqlhce.com/click-3631793-10480883" target="_top">5% Off Any New York Pass! Use Coupon Code: nyp5pc2007</a><img src="http://www.awltovhc.com/image-3631793-10480883" border="0" alt="" width="1" height="1" /></p>\r\n<p>Check out the <a href="http://www.tkqlhce.com/click-3631793-10780040" target="_top">Gray Line Night on the Town Tour!</a><img src="http://www.lduhtrp.net/image-3631793-10780040" border="0" alt="" width="1" height="1" /></p>\r\n<p>Take an unforgettable trip that''s full of <a href="http://www.anrdoezrs.net/click-3631793-10515268" target="_top">NYC Sightseeing</a><img src="http://www.ftjcfx.com/image-3631793-10515268" border="0" alt="" width="1" height="1" /></p>\r\n<p>See the best <a href="http://www.dpbolvw.net/click-3631793-10515273" target="_top">New York City Attractions</a><img src="http://www.tqlkg.com/image-3631793-10515273" border="0" alt="" width="1" height="1" /></p>\r\n<p>Planning a trip to NYC? Take along the <a href="http://www.kqzyfj.com/click-3631793-9760727" target="_top">New York Pass</a><img src="http://www.awltovhc.com/image-3631793-9760727" border="0" alt="" width="1" height="1" /></p>\r\n<p>Don''t miss out on the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.dpbolvw.net/click-3631793-10619033" target="_top">Super New York Tour</a><img src="http://www.ftjcfx.com/image-3631793-10619033" border="0" alt="" width="1" height="1" /></p>\r\n<p>NYC tours are fun for the whole family&nbsp;<a href="http://www.anrdoezrs.net/click-3631793-10510687" target="_top">New York City Tours and Sightseeing</a><img src="http://www.ftjcfx.com/image-3631793-10510687" border="0" alt="" width="1" height="1" /></p>\r\n<p>Visit the Big Apple&nbsp;<a href="http://www.jdoqocy.com/click-3631793-10761698" target="_top">New York City Tours</a><img src="http://www.ftjcfx.com/image-3631793-10761698" border="0" alt="" width="1" height="1" /></p>\r\n<p>Discounts on Gray Line tours&nbsp;<a href="http://www.kqzyfj.com/click-3631793-10783455" target="_top">Take $5 Off - Gray Line New York&nbsp;</a><img src="http://www.tqlkg.com/image-3631793-10783455" border="0" alt="" width="1" height="1" /></p>\r\n<p>See more with the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.kqzyfj.com/click-3631793-10761704" target="_top">Gray Line New York All Loops Tour</a><img src="http://www.lduhtrp.net/image-3631793-10761704" border="0" alt="" width="1" height="1" /></p>\r\n{{ADSPACE_300_250}}\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Visit unique attractions, world-famous museums, theaters, skyscrapers and more. Check out bus tours and helicopter tours as well! ', 'sight seeing , visit new york, new york sightseeing, sightseeing tours, central park sightseeing, tours of central park, visit central park, statue of liberty, grand central, helicopter tour, multi-lingual tours, bilingual tours, tours in spanish, tours in portuguese, tours in german, tours in dutch, tours in russian, tours in italian, tours in turkish, photography tours', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', 'bethesda.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, '', '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(466, '2013-08-20', 0, 1, 15, 'Vibe FAQ', '', 'vibe-faq', 'Vibe FAQ', '<dl> <dt><strong>What is Vibe @ Central Park?</strong></dt> <dd>It''s a way to anonymously share thoughts and pictures on your mobile phone with other people in Central Park without knowing who they are in advance. Vibe is both a communication medium and also a community of people around the world.</dd> <dt><strong>Why would I want to talk to strangers?</strong></dt> <dd>You can use Vibe to ask questions and share thoughts &amp; experiences while you''re in Central Park (or anywhere, really). You can even meet new people and potentially make new friends! Vibes are anonymous so you can be completely honest (but please be considerate).</dd> <dt><strong>How do I vibe?</strong></dt> <dd>You can post and reply to "vibes" using texts and pictures. </dd>\r\n{{ADSPACE_300_250}}\r\n<dt><strong>Do I have to register or login to vibe?</strong></dt> <dd>No, there is no registration or login to use Vibe. It is quick and easy to use.</dd> <dt><strong>Can I Tweet my vibes? </strong></dt> <dd>Yes, it''s easy to tweet your vibes to your Twitter followers. Simply select "Tweet your reply" when you create your vibe. </dd> <dt><strong>Does Vibe work outside of Central Park?</strong></dt> <dd>Yes, vibes are visible from 150 feet to 31 miles from wherever you are located in the world. </dd> <dt><strong>How long will my vibe post stay up?</strong></dt> <dd>Your vibe can last from 15 minutes to 30 days (you choose when it expires).</dd> </dl>', 'Vibe @ Central Park is a way to anonymously share thoughts and pictures on your mobile phone with other people in Central Park without knowing who they are in advance.', '', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', 'great_lawn_rick.jpg', '<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/about-centralpark-com/staff/rick-anderson.html">Rick Anderson</a>', '', '', 0, '', '', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', 'Vibe FAQ', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(467, '2014-08-05', 397, 2, 14, 'Ceremony Packages FAQs', '', 'weddings/faqs/ceremony-packages', 'Ceremony Packages FAQs - Weddings in Central Park', '<dl class="faqScrollable"> <dt><strong>Q: What are the different package options for my ceremony?</strong></dt> <dd>\r\n<p>A: I Do New York offers 3 different all-inclusive package options for you to choose from: Intimate, Celebrate, and Elegance. You can choose whichever best suits your needs for your special day!</p>\r\n<p>Follow this link to see what each package entails:</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/weddings/ceremony-packages.html">http://www.centralpark.com/guide/weddings/ceremony-packages.html</a></p>\r\n</dd> <dt><strong>Q: Can I customize my package?</strong></dt> <dd>\r\n<p>A: Any package can be customized for your ceremony based on your needs. It is best to choose the package that most closely reflects what you would like to have included in your ceremony.</p>\r\n</dd> <dt><strong>Q: How do I pay for my package?</strong></dt> <dd>\r\n<p>A: All payments are made through PayPal. After choosing the package that best suits your needs, you make the initial 5% deposit of the package price by following the link below and selecting your package for purchase.</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/weddings/ceremony-packages.html">http://www.centralpark.com/guide/weddings/ceremony-packages.html</a></p>\r\n<p>Two months prior to your ceremony, a payment of 70% of the total package price is due. I Do New York will send you a payment request through PayPal, to your e-mail at that time.</p>\r\n<p>Two weeks prior to your ceremony, the final payment for the package is due. Once again, I Do New York will send you a payment request through PayPal, to your e-mail at that time.</p>\r\n</dd></dl>\r\n{{ADSPACE_300_250}}\r\n<dl class="faqScrollable"><dt><strong>Q: How do I choose my vendors?</strong></dt> <dd>\r\n<p>A: One of the most important aspects of planning your ceremony is choosing the people who will create your ideal ceremony. We work with you and what you envision for your ceremony to find the perfect match for each aspect of your ceremony. I Do New York employs the best that New York City has to offer for your wedding day. Any booking of vendors is done through I Do New York.</p>\r\n<p>The most important things to choose for your wedding are listed below.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Officiant</strong>: Whether of a religious affiliation, non-denominational, or non-religious, we can provide you with an officiant that best reflects the expression of your love and commitment in your ceremony.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Photography</strong>: Photographs of your wedding ceremony provide you with memories that you can cherish forever. What better way to remember your special ceremony in Central Park than with the help of one of our great photographers?</p>\r\n<p><strong>Flowers</strong>: Choosing your floral arrangements can be very personal and specific. We can work with you to create in-season floral arrangements of your choice.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Musicians</strong>: Music can provide the perfect backdrop and mood to any ceremony. Although there is no amplified sound allowed in Central Park, the acoustic musician options are endless. From violin to acoustic guitar and so on, we can put together the songs and sounds that you so desire. You have the option of a single acoustic musician, a duet, or even a quartet!</p>\r\n</dd> <dt><strong>Q: Do I have a wedding planner?</strong></dt> <dd>\r\n<p>A: Yes! Our wedding planner will guide you through the whole process of planning your ceremony. With the beauty of today&rsquo;s technology, we work with you through e-mail correspondence during our office hours: Monday through Friday, from 9AM to 5PM EST.</p>\r\n</dd> <dt><strong>Q: When do I get to meet with my wedding planner?</strong></dt> <dd>\r\n<p>A: Typically every couple meets with the I Do New York wedding planner in person to perform a walk-through of your ceremony and on the day of your wedding.</p>\r\n</dd> </dl>', 'Here you can find all of the answers to our most frequently asked questions about having a wedding in Central Park.', 'wedding package, ceremony package, wedding planner', 0.00, 0, '<script type=''text/javascript''><!--//<![CDATA[\r\n   var m3_u = (location.protocol==''https:''?''https://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'':''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ajs.php'');\r\n   var m3_r = Math.floor(Math.random()*99999999999);\r\n   if (!document.MAX_used) document.MAX_used = '','';\r\n   document.write ("<scr"+"ipt type=''text/javascript'' src=''"+m3_u);\r\n   document.write ("?zoneid=12&blockcampaign=1");\r\n   document.write (''&cb='' + m3_r);\r\n   if (document.MAX_used != '','') document.write ("&exclude=" + document.MAX_used);\r\n   document.write ("&loc=" + escape(window.location));\r\n   if (document.referrer) document.write ("&referer=" + escape(document.referrer));\r\n   if (document.context) document.write ("&context=" + escape(document.context));\r\n   if (document.mmm_fo) document.write ("&mmm_fo=1");\r\n   document.write ("''></scr"+"ipt>");\r\n//]]>--></script><noscript><a href=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/ck.php?n=ab1f636b&cb=1233'' target=''_blank''><img src=''http://ads.centralpark.com/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=12&n=ab1f636b'' border=''0'' alt='''' /></a></noscript>', '', '', '', 'weddings-in-central-park.jpg', 'Fotovolia', '', '', 3, '', '', 0, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Ceremony Packages', 'Ceremony Packages FAQs', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
