 hunt, weddings, concerts, concert, aa-map, family-map, aa-podcast, family-podcast, Bow Bridge, Central Park Maps, Great Lawn, reservoir, running track, Sheep Meadow, Strawberry Fields, Tavern on the Green, tours, walking tours, Wollman Rink', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', 'weddings-in-central-park.jpg', 'Fotovolia', '', '', 3, '/usr/media/weddings.v2/weddings.v2.css', '', 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Elegance Renewal', 'Elegance Renewal', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(494, '2014-09-23', 447, 2, 7, 'Hidden Secrets Walking Tour', '', 'tours/walking/hidden-secrets-tour', 'Hidden Secrets of Central Park Walking Tour', '<div id="toursWrapper">\r\n<h1 class="walkingTour title">Hidden Secrets Walking Tour</h1>\r\n<p>Take a walk on the road less traveled in Central Park and discover its hidden gems! Tour the hard to find places that most people don''t ever get to see.<span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>Central Park''s 843 acres are a challenge to cover on your own. Together with your knowledgeable tour guide you''ll experience some of the lesser-known treasures and see&nbsp;just how full of history and natural beauty that Central Park really is.</p>\r\n<script src="https://fareharbor.com/embeds/script/calendar-small/smyrnatours/items/1300,1348/?lightframe=yes&amp;asn=centralpark"></script>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>The starting point of the tour is at the entrance of <a href="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=central+park+west+and+West+96th+Street,++New+York,+NY&amp;hl=ro&amp;sll=40.792207,-73.967664&amp;sspn=0.008318,0.01929&amp;hnear=Central+Park+West+%26+W+96th+St,+New+York,+10025&amp;t=m&amp;z=16&amp;iwloc=A" target="_blank">Central Park West &amp; W. 96th Street</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n{{ADSPACE_300_250}}\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>CANCELLATION POLICY</h3>\r\n<p>If any scheduled walking tours are canceled due to bad weather conditions, you may choose to postpone the day service is given or request a full refund.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>24 hours prior cancellation</strong>: You may choose to postpone the day service is given or request a full refund.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Same day cancellation</strong>: You may choose to postpone the day service is given or request a refund with a 50% cancellation penalty.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Last hour cancellation:</strong>&nbsp;If you need to cancel your tour within the last hour, no refund or postpone will be provided.</p>\r\n<p>If you would like cancel or make changes to your reservation, please call +1 (347) 871-4499.</p>\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>', 'Take a walk off the beaten path in Central Park and discover its less-traveled hidden gems!', 'secrets of central park tour, central park group tour, central park group walking tour, central park walking tour, walking tour, secret tour of central park, central park tour, hidden secrets of central park, central park uncommon locations, cool central park tour, unique central park tour, tours of central park', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 3, '/usr/media/tours.v2/tours.css', '/usr/media/tours.v2/tours.js', 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Hidden Secrets', 'Hidden Secrets', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(496, '2013-01-04', 447, 2, 14, 'Downtown & Wall Street Tour', '', 'tours/walking-tours/downtown-wall-street-tour', 'Downtown & Wall Street Tour | Central Park Tours', '<div id="toursWrapper">\r\n<h1 class="walkingTourDws title">Downtown &amp; Wall Street Walking Tour</h1>\r\n<table style="background: #fff; margin-left: 10px;" border="0" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><img src="/usr/media/tours.v2/dws.jpg" border="0" alt="Downtown and Wall Street Walking Tour" width="150" height="226" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>It''s a triple header! See the Downtown Area, Wall Street and Ground Zero/Freedom Tower. Learn about the birth of Manhattan and its amazing history. There are over 15 different sites to see! We start with the oldest parts of the city and continue to the Freedom Tower. Hear first hand stories from your tour guide about what it was like to be&nbsp;at Ground Zero.</p>\r\n<p>We will meet and start in <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=Battery+Park,+New+York+Plaza,+New+York,+NY,+United+States&amp;hl=en&amp;ll=40.703155,-74.012575&amp;spn=0.023132,0.055747&amp;sll=40.767117,-73.983859&amp;sspn=0.000759,0.001742&amp;oq=Battery+Park+New+York&amp;t=h&amp;hq=Battery+Park,+New+York+Plaza,+New+York,+NY,+United+States&amp;z=15">Battery Park</a>. <strong>Directions:</strong> Take the 1 train to South Ferry (last stop), or the R to Whitehall.<span>You can also take the 5 to Bowling Green and walk over.</span></p>\r\n<div style="float: right; margin: 0 0 5px 5px;"><a href="/tours/downtown-wallstreet-walking-tour"><img src="/usr/media/tours.v2/reserve-online-walking.png" alt="Reserve Online" /></a></div>\r\n<p>Offered Monday through Saturday at 2:30pm.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><strong>This tour covers:</strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Battery Park</li>\r\n<li>Castle Clinton</li>\r\n<li>The Sphere sculpture</li>\r\n<li>Customs House</li>\r\n<li>Bowling Green Park</li>\r\n<li>Canyon of Heroes</li>\r\n<li>Trinity Church</li>\r\n<li>Wall Street</li>\r\n<li>New York Stock Exchange</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 50%;">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Federal Hall</li>\r\n<li>House of Morgan</li>\r\n<li>40 Wall Street</li>\r\n<li>Zuccotti Park (birth of the Occupy Wall Street movement)</li>\r\n<li>Woolworth Building</li>\r\n<li>City Hall</li>\r\n<li>St. Paul''s Chapel</li>\r\n<li>Ground Zero/ Memorial</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class="pricing" border="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<thead> \r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="col-1">No. of persons</td>\r\n<td class="col-2">Price\r\n<div><small>(per person)</small></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class="col-3">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead> \r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="col-1" colspan="3">\r\n<h3>3-HOUR LONG TOUR <br /><small>Time offered: Mon - Sat 2:30pm</small></h3>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="col-1">1 person</td>\r\n<td class="col-2">$80</td>\r\n<td class="col-3" rowspan="8"><a href="/tours/downtown-wall-street-walking-tour?duration=0">Reserve Now &rsaquo;</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="col-1">2 persons</td>\r\n<td class="col-2">$65</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="col-1">3 persons</td>\r\n<td class="col-2">$60</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="col-1">4 persons</td>\r\n<td class="col-2">$55</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="col-1">5-10 persons</td>\r\n<td class="col-2">$50</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="col-1">11-20 persons</td>\r\n<td class="col-2">$45</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="col-1">20+ persons</td>\r\n<td class="col-2">$40</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="col-1">30+ kids</td>\r\n<td class="col-2">$35</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div><strong>Note:</strong> The minimum price for a single person is the price for two persons.<br />Please <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/contact">contact us</a> for any last minute reservation changes.</div>\r\n</div>', 'See the Downtown Area, Wall Street and Ground Zero/Freedom Tower. Learn about the birth of Manhattan and its amazing history.', 'wall street, ground zero, freedom tower, downtown, manhattan, battery park', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 4, '/usr/media/tours.v2/tours.css', '/usr/media/tours.v2/tours.js', 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Downtown & Wall Street', 'Downtown & Wall Street', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
