(517, '2015-07-29', 447, 2, 15, 'Arts & Architecture Tours', '', 'tours/walking/arts-architecture-tours', 'Arts & Architecture Tours | Central Park Tours', '<div id="toursWrapper">\r\n<h1 class="artsArchitectureTour title">Arts &amp; Architecture Tour</h1>\r\n<p>Find out what makes Central Park so special and inspiring on this on this unique walking tour as you learn about the thought and meaning that was put into many of the different buildings, monuments, works of art and lay of the land in Central Park.</p>\r\n<script src="https://fareharbor.com/embeds/script/calendar-small/smyrnatours/items/1298,1345,1299,1347,1307/?lightframe=yes&amp;asn=centralpark"></script>\r\n<div>Tours run every hour from 9:00 am to 6:00 pm. Depending on your walking speed, the 2 hour tour covers about 1/2 of the park,&nbsp;<a href="#aa-nc">North</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href="#aa-sc">South,</a>&nbsp;in approximately 2 to 2 1/2 hours.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;"><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;">{{ADSPACE_300_250}}</span></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br />\r\n<p><span style="font-weight: bold;">Custom Tour</span></p>\r\n<p>You can also request a custom tour with us. Please specify what you are looking for in the comments section of the reservation form and we will be happy to work with you. Pricing for custom tours will vary on time and locations wanted.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>WHERE THE TOUR MEETS</h3>\r\n<p>The starting point of the tour is at&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.it/maps/place/208+W+80th+St,+New+York,+NY+10024,+USA/@40.784164,-73.978586,18z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x89c258889f0b8a25:0x1d5bc9700a3c1264!6m1!1e1" target="_blank">208 W. 80th Street, New York, NY 10024</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p id="aa-nc"><strong>NORTH-CENTER TOUR ATTRACTIONS</strong></p>\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Belvedere Castle</li>\r\n<li>Conservatory Garden</li>\r\n<li>Conservatory Water</li>\r\n<li>Delacorte Music Clock</li>\r\n<li>Delacorte Theater</li>\r\n<li>Gapstow Bridge</li>\r\n<li>Greyshot Arch</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Heckscher Ballfields</li>\r\n<li>Loeb Boathouse</li>\r\n<li>Reservoir</li>\r\n<li>Shakespeare Garden</li>\r\n<li>Swedish Cottage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<p id="aa-sc"><strong>SOUTH-CENTER TOUR ATTRACTIONS</strong></p>\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Balto</li>\r\n<li>Bandshell</li>\r\n<li>Bethesda Terrace</li>\r\n<li>Bethesda Fountain</li>\r\n<li>Carousel</li>\r\n<li>Cherry Hill</li>\r\n<li>Children''s Zoo</li>\r\n<li>Dairy</li>\r\n<li>Dakota</li>\r\n<li>Essex House</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Grand Army Plaza</li>\r\n<li>Heckscher Playground</li>\r\n<li>The Lake</li>\r\n<li>The Mall</li>\r\n<li>Sheep Meadow</li>\r\n<li>Strawberry Fields</li>\r\n<li>SummerStage</li>\r\n<li>Tavern on the Green</li>\r\n<li>Victorian Gardens</li>\r\n<li>Wollman Rink</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class="sep"><a href="#toursWrapper">Back to top &uarr;</a></div>\r\n<h3>CANCELLATION POLICY</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">If any scheduled walking tours are canceled due to bad weather conditions, you may choose to postpone the day service is given or request a full refund.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>24 hours prior cancellation</strong>: You may choose to postpone the day service is given or request a full refund.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Same day cancellation</strong>: You may choose to postpone the day service is given or request a refund with a 50% cancellation penalty.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Last hour cancellation:</strong>&nbsp;If you need to cancel your tour within the last hour, no refund or postpone will be provided.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">If you would like cancel or make changes to your reservation, please call +1 (347) 871-4499.</p>\r\n<div class="sep"><a href="#toursWrapper">Back to top &uarr;</a></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Find out what makes Central Park so special and inspiring on a unique walking tour that focuses on its arts and architecture. ', 'architecture tours, arts tours, central park tours, art walking tours, central park architecture, architecture walking tours, Belvedere Castle, Conservatory Garden, Gapstow Bridge, Shakespeare Garden, Loeb Boathouse', 0.00, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '/usr/media/tours.v2/tours.css', '/usr/media/tours.v2/tours.js', 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'Arts & Architecture Tour', 'Arts & Architecture Tour', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(518, '2015-07-29', 447, 2, 15, 'Movie & TV Sites Tours', '', 'tours/walking/movie-tv-sites-tours', 'Movie & TV Sites Tours | Central Park Tours', '<div id="toursWrapper">\r\n<h1 class="movieTvTour title">Movie &amp; TV Sites Tours</h1>\r\n<p>Experience a piece of Hollywood in Central Park and visit the locations where famous movies and tv shows and scenes were shot, such as&nbsp;Ghostbusters, Home Alone 2, Spiderman 3, Maid in Manhattan, Enchanted, Friends, Sex in the City, Saturday Night Live, Gossip Girl, 30 Rock, and many more.</p>\r\n<p>Your tour guide can also point out to you where many celebrities live around the park.</p>\r\n<script src="https://fareharbor.com/embeds/script/calendar-small/smyrnatours/items/1298,1345,1299,1347,1307/?lightframe=yes&amp;asn=centralpark"></script>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Tours run every hour from 9:00 am to 6:00 pm. Depending on your walking speed, the 2 hour tour covers about 1/2 of the park,&nbsp;<a href="#tv-nc">North</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href="#tv-sc">South,</a>&nbsp;in approximately 2 to 2 1/2 hours.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;"><span style="background: #efefef; color: green; padding: 2px;">{{ADSPACE_300_250}}</span></span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>WHERE THE TOUR MEETS</h3>\r\n<p>The starting point of the tour is at&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.it/maps/place/208+W+80th+St,+New+York,+NY+10024,+USA/@40.784164,-73.978586,18z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x89c258889f0b8a25:0x1d5bc9700a3c1264!6m1!1e1" target="_blank">208 W. 80th Street, New York, NY 10024</a>.</p>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<big><strong>Custom Tour</strong></big>\r\n<p>You can also request a custom tour with us. Please specify what you are looking for in the comments section of the reservation form and we will be happy to work with you. Pricing for custom tours will vary on time and locations wanted.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p id="tv-nc"><strong>NORTH-CENTER TOUR ATTRACTIONS</strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cel