(557, '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 0, 'Activities', '', NULL, 'Central Park Activities', '<p>Central Park has something for everyone, no matter your interests or the time of the year that you choose to visit. Here are a few suggestions for some things to do:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table align="right" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="3" style="background:#ffffff">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<table align="right" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #ffffff; width:200px">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td><img alt="Horse-Drawn Carriage" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/horse.jpg" style="width:200px" /></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td><strong>Horse-Drawn Carriage Ride</strong> by <em><a href="http://www.centralpark.com/members/profile2306.html">sdwxh</a></em></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h2>THINGS TO DO YEAR ROUND</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Throughout the year you can take a <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/tours.html">guided tour</a> of the park in a <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/tours/horse-carriage-tours.html">horse-drawn carriage</a>, <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/tours/pedicab.html">pedicab tour</a>&nbsp;or on a <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/tours/bike/guided.html">bike tour</a>, or if you&#39;re feeling independent you can <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/tours/bike-rentals.html">rent a bike</a> and tour around on your own.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Visit the <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/central-park-zoo.html">Central Park Zoo</a> or take a self-guided <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/walking-tours.html">walking tour</a> to familiarize yourself with some of the more well-known spots in the Park.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also have your own&nbsp;<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/activities/weddings.html?utm_source=activities&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=weddings">wedding in the park</a>, stage a dream <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/weddings/proposals.html" title="proposal central park">proposal</a>, <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/weddings/vow-renewals.html" title="vow renewal central park">renew your wedding vows</a>,&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/special-events.html?utm_source=activities&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=special_events">hold a special event</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For families, there are plenty of&nbsp;<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/activities/children-s-activities.html">things to do with kids</a>&nbsp;and over 20 <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/activities/children-s-activities/playgrounds.html">children&#39;s playgrounds</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are also a myriad of <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/sports.html">sports</a>&nbsp;such as <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/sports/baseball-and-softball.html" title="baseball central park">baseball</a>, <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/sports/tennis.html" title="tennis central park">tennis</a> and <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/sports/running.html" title="running central park">running</a> that can be played in Central Park anytime.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:green"><span style="color:green">{{ADSPACE_300_250}}</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>SPRING &amp; SUMMER</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>During the warmer months there are <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/activities/concerts.html">concerts</a> presented by <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/activities/concerts/summerstage-festival.html">SummerStage</a>, <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/activities/concerts/gma-concerts.html">Good Morning America</a>, <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/activities/concerts/new-york-philharmonic.html">The New York Philharmonic</a> and <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/activities/concerts.html">others</a> featuring a wide variety of genres for all music-lovers.</p>\r\n\r\n<table align="right" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="3" style="margin:10px 0 5px 5px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<table align="right" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td><img alt="Bow Bridge Picnic" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/activities/bow-bridge-picnic.jpg" style="width:200px" title="Bow Bridge Picnic" /></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td><a href="http://www.centralparkpicnic.com/best-areas-central-park/cherry-hill-bow-bridge-mid-park-72nd" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="Picnic Central Park">Picnic in Central Park</a></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td>\r\n						<p><span style="font-size:xx-small"><strong>Bow Bridge Picnic.</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n						<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n						</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>Seasonal plays and events like&nbsp;<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/activities/shakespeare-in-the-park.html">Shakespeare in the Park</a> and the <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/activities/movies.html">Central Park Film Festival</a>&nbsp;are much-anticipated annual activities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Take a <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/events/show/2289/yoga-101-the-yoga-trail-in-central-park" title="central park yoga">relaxing yoga class</a>&nbsp;on the grass or have a&nbsp;<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/activities/picnics.html">have a picnic</a>&nbsp;with some friends.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>See the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/cherry-trees.html" title="cherry blossom trees">cherry blossom trees</a>&nbsp;throughout Central Park and visit many other beautiful flowers and plants inside of the <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/attractions/conservatory-garden.html" title="conservatory garden central park">Conservatory Garden</a>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>FALL &amp; WINTER</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table align="left" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="3" style="background:#ffffff">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<table align="right" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% #ffffff; width:200px">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td><a href="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/activities/ice-skating-in-central-park.jpg" rel="lightbox-guire" title="Ice Skating at Wollman Rink"><img alt="Ice Skating" src="http://www.centralpark.com/updata/Image/ice-skating-in-central-park.jpg" style="width:200px" /> </a></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td><strong>Ice Skating at Wollman Rink</strong><br />\r\n						by <em><a href="http://www.centralpark.com/members/profile12813.html">Tim4Peace</a></em></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>During the colder months, many people like to go <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/pages/sports/ice-skating.html">ice skating </a>at Wollman or Lasker Rink.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/tours/walking-tours/holiday-sights-tour.html" title="holiday sights walking tour central park new york">Holiday Sights walking tour</a> is a great way to see both a bit of Central Park and the surrounding areas of NYC that are all lit up with decorations and festivities during the holiday season.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also check out our list of <a href="http://www.centralpark.com/guide/activities/fun-fall-and-winter-traditions.html" title="fun fall and winter activities in central park">fun fall &amp; winter activities</a>&nbsp;for other ideas of what to do when it&#39;s a bit more chilly in Central Park.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Find out about things to do in Central Park like concerts, SummerStage, events, Shakespeare In the Park, horse & carriage rides, the Central Park Film Festival, running, bike rentals, ice skating, and more.', 'central park activities, activities in central park, activities in central park new york, shakespeare in the park, new york theatre, summer stage, joe''s pub in the park, great lawn, things to do in central park, what to do in central park, concerts in central park, music in central park, tours in central park, central park tours, central park yoga, central park wedding, central park concert, central park sightseeing, central park ice skating, SummerStage, central park events, horse & carriage rides, Central Park Film Festival, running, bike rentals, ice skating', 0.00, 0, NULL, NULL, '', '', 'deafult.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, '', '', 0, '2015-09-02 11:39:23', '2015-09-02 11:39:23');
